INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (2,'Whey Gold Standard (2.27kg)','GOLD STANDARD 100% WHEY™ Protein powder supports muscle and post-workout recovery with 24g of quality protein and 5.5g of naturally occurring BCAAs per serving¹.\r\nIt’s crafted to be a complete, fast-digesting protein with whey protein isolate as the primary source – a filtered form of whey that can support protein goals for people at every level of fitness – from daily runners and gym-goers to competitive strength athletes and everyone in between.',80.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-08-21 17:56:27','2025-05-26 20:13:40'),(3,'Nitro Tech whey protein (1.8kg)','It’s clean and simple – and it delivers. A single scoop of Nitro-Tech® contains 30g of protein, 3g of creatine monohydrate & 6.6g of BCAAs , primarily from whey protein peptides and whey isolate, two of the cleanest and purest proteins.',60.00,1,1,0.00,'2024-08-21 18:27:46','2025-05-26 20:12:46'),(5,'Nitro Tech whey gold (907g)','It’s clean and simple – and it delivers. A single scoop of Nitro-Tech® contains 24g of protein, 4g Glutamine & 5.3g of BCAAs (28 servings) , primarily from whey protein peptides and whey isolate, two of the cleanest and purest proteins.',35.00,1,0,0.00,'2024-08-21 18:43:57','2025-03-27 16:17:39'),(6,'Challenger Nutrition 100% Whey Protein (66 servings)','24 grams protein • Produced through microfiltration technique for purity • Absorbs quickly into the body for maximum performance • Fuels working muscles and stimulates protein synthesis. 2.26 kg and 66 servings.',60.00,1,0,0.00,'2024-08-21 18:56:39','2025-04-10 18:40:58'),(7,'BPI Whey HD','150 Calories Per Scoop\r\n25g Protein Per Scoop\r\n5g BCAAs Per Scoop\r\nHigh Quality Whey \r\nLow Carb \r\nLow Sugar',50.00,1,1,0.00,'2024-08-21 19:13:28','2025-04-08 16:58:16'),(9,'Scitec Nutrition  100% whey protein','10 gram EAAs per serving , 21 gram protein per serving , gluten-free , no added sugar , 2350 gram , 78 servings.\r\n1 or 2 scoops daily to help you hit your protein goal.',75.00,1,1,0.00,'2024-08-21 19:34:56','2024-08-22 16:02:09'),(11,'Scitec Nutrition  muscle pro','100% Whey Protein* Professional\r\nwith extra amino acids\r\nwith digestive enzymes\r\nwith instant whey proteins\r\ngluten-free\r\nLactose-free\r\n3g Creatine\r\n2500 gram\r\n83 servings\r\n23 gram protein per serving',85.00,1,1,6.00,'2024-08-21 19:56:42','2024-08-22 16:04:09'),(12,'mp combat protein powder','52 servings ,  \r\nEach serving of Combat Protein Powder delivers a commanding 25 grams of protein, fueling your muscle to ensure your hard work and dedication yield real results.\r\n\r\nCombat Protein is the athlete\'s complete protein. Masterfully engineered with a premium blend of 5 unique protein sources, including high-quality whey protein powder, protein powder isolate, hydrolysate and concentrate, egg albumin, and milk protein concentrate. Each protein source digests at a different rate. Varying digestion rates, provide comprehensive amino acid infusion. This strategic approach is crucial for efficient muscle growth and recovery.',55.00,1,0,0.00,'2024-08-21 20:04:19','2025-05-12 16:35:26'),(13,'2 gold creatine + shaker','2 gold creatine + shaker \r\neach creatine contains 60 servings',35.00,5,0,0.00,'2024-08-21 20:09:26','2025-04-19 20:19:36'),(14,'2 whey hd + gold creatine','2 whey hd + gold creatine\r\neach container of whey hd contains 50 servings.\r\n each container of gold creatine contains 60 servings.',110.00,5,1,0.00,'2024-08-21 20:15:58','2024-08-22 16:05:58'),(15,'2 nitrotech','2 nitrotech whey protien .\r\nContact us to choose your flavor after checkout.',99.00,5,1,0.00,'2024-08-21 20:24:15','2024-08-22 16:06:24'),(16,'Bpi iso hd','BPI SPORTS ISO HD Combines delicious flavors, with a premium whey isolate. Crafted for easy digestion and absorption, and easily dissolvable. ISO HD is perfect for your protein shakes or any of your delicious protein recipes! You do not have to sacrifice taste in order to get a premium protein. Let ISO HD show you how protein should be!\r\n\r\n25g of Whey Protein With Each Scoop\r\nExtremely easy to digest & no stomach bloat afterwards\r\nIncredibly Reviewed Flavors!\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS: WHEY PROTEIN ISOLATE, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS, NON-DAIRY CREAMER, SALT, SOY AND SUNFLOWER LECITHIN, CELLULOSE GUM, SUCRALOSE, AND ACESULFAME-K.\r\n\r\nMANUFACTURED IN A FACILITY THAT ALSO PROCESSES EGG AND TREE NUTS.',65.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-08-21 22:08:17','2025-02-07 18:16:47'),(25,'Challenger Nutrition whey isolate','• 25 grams protein, 0 sugar, 0 fat • Produced through micro-filtration technique for purity • Absorbs quickly into the body for maximum performance • Fuels working muscles and stimulates protein synthesis •',80.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-08-22 16:48:22','2025-03-10 14:31:27'),(26,'Mass gainer offer','Mass gainer 6kg 0 fat 0 sugar \r\nCreatine mono 60 servings \r\nFree shaker',80.00,5,1,0.00,'2024-08-22 17:26:13','2025-03-13 20:40:27'),(27,'ISO 100','One of the highest-quality protein powders in the game, it’s filtered to remove excess lactose, carbs, fat, and sugar for maximum mixability and gains. Don’t just beat your best. Smash right through it with the amazing taste of ISO100 Cookies & Cream.',95.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-08-22 17:45:10','2025-02-07 18:17:36'),(28,'Isoflex 100% Pure Whey Protein Isolate (2.27kg)','Truly Superior Whey Protein Isolate\r\nWhey Isolate Protein Technology\r\nGluten-Free & Soy-Free\r\nSugar-Free & Fat Free\r\nLactose-Free\r\nKosher\r\nLab-Tested\r\n100% Whey Isolate Protein',105.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-08-22 18:03:21','2025-04-11 18:55:04'),(29,'Isoflex 100% Pure Whey Protein Isolate 30 servings (2lbs)','Truly Superior Whey Protein Isolate\r\nWhey Isolate Protein Technology\r\nGluten-Free & Soy-Free\r\nSugar-Free & Fat Free\r\nLactose-Free\r\nKosher\r\nLab-Tested\r\n100% Whey Isolate Protein',55.00,2,0,12.00,'2024-08-22 20:34:25','2024-09-12 20:25:27'),(30,'LEVRONE GOLD CREATINE (300g)','Supplementing the diet with creatine, recommended for adults performing high intensity exercise. Creatine increases physical performance in successive bursts of short-term, high intensity exercise, beneficial efect is obtained with a daily intake of 5 g of creatine. Vitamin B6 contributes to the normal function of the immune system',18.00,3,0,0.00,'2024-08-22 21:59:56','2025-04-15 14:37:14'),(31,'ALL MAX Creatine Monohydrate Powder (400g)','Micronized Pharmaceutical Grade Creatine Monohydrate for Bodybuilding\r\nImproves Performance in Short-Burst, High Intensity Training\r\nHelps Increase Muscle Mass, Strength and Size\r\nThe World’s Most Studied and Proven Supplement \r\n80 SERVINGS',35.00,3,1,0.00,'2024-08-22 22:51:58','2025-04-11 18:58:00'),(32,'Challenger Nutrition creatine (300g)','• Enhances muscle production and growth\r\n\r\n• Improves training performance and endurance\r\n\r\n• Helps delay fatigue\r\n\r\n• Boosts energy during workouts and all day\r\n\r\n• Easy and convenient powder that mixes well\r\n\r\nCreatine is a powerful compound that supports the production of energy within hardworking muscles. Challenger Nutrition’s Creatine Powder 5000mg is a rich source of creatine monohydrate to help you improve your protein metabolism, volumize your body cells, and increase the production of secretion of Human Growth Hormone (HGH). Not only that, but it also breaks the weakness of muscle tissues, leaving you with extra energy and a better muscular shape. \r\n\r\nOur creatine monohydrate powder boosts the body’s ability to perform with high intensity and builds muscle mass and strength. This is an essential supplement for weight lifters and bodybuilders who are looking to build muscle, but also endurance athletes, such as cyclists, who want to improve muscle performance during exercise.\r\n\r\nScientifically, creatine is a molecule in creatine phosphate that produce energy to support healthy cellular function. It is a naturally occurring component in your body, and it needs just a few seconds to reprocess after supplementation and fill your muscles with energy.\r\n\r\nIf you aren’t getting enough creatine in your diet from food alone to support your workouts, our creatine powder is a must for hardworking challengers like you. When your muscles are completely saturated with creatine through supplementation, you feel more energy and experience increased lean muscle growth.\r\n\r\nTo use, just mix a scoop (5 grams) of Challenger Nutrition creatine monohydrate powder into 8 to 12 ounces of water, juice, or your favorite beverage. What sets our creatine powder apart from all the others on the market is its exceptional potency and purity. We’ve also specially formulated our creatine to mix better and stay suspended for longer in liquid so that you reap its benefits with none of the aftertaste that other products leave behind.',30.00,3,1,15.00,'2024-08-22 23:03:21','2024-08-23 00:40:14'),(33,'BPI Sports Micronized Creatine (120 servings)','BPI Sports Micronized Creatine - Increase Strength - Reduce Fatigue - Lean Muscle Building - 100% Pure Creatine - Better Absorption - Supports Muscle Growth - Unflavored - 120 Servings',35.00,3,0,0.00,'2024-08-22 23:27:10','2025-05-26 20:34:09'),(34,'Creatine monohydrate 300g  (60 servings)','Elevate your fitness game with micronized CREATINE MONOHYDRATE – a true powerhouse for aiding in muscle and strength enhancement. Boasting a legacy as one of the most extensively studied, proven, and sought-after fitness enhancers - creatine continues to reign supreme. CREATINE MONOHYDRATE powder features the premium micronized version of creatine monohydrate for superior mixability and rapid absorption that won’t cause bloating or discomfort. Experience the full spectrum of creatine\'s power - increase your performance, build explosive strength, and show off those impressive lean muscle gains.',20.00,3,1,0.00,'2024-08-22 23:31:50','2025-05-26 20:34:18'),(35,'PLATINUM 100% CREATINE 400g (80 servings)','PLATINUM 100% CREATINE PROVIDES ULTRA-PURE MICRONIZED CREATINE POWDER\r\nPlatinum 100% Creatine provides your muscles with the world’s highest quality and most clinically researched form of micronized creatine. Creatine is shown to increase lean muscle and improve strength and endurance.',35.00,3,1,0.00,'2024-08-22 23:36:05','2025-05-26 20:39:49'),(36,'ANABOLIC PEAK (5.4kg)','1330 CALORIES\r\n60G OF PROTEIN \r\n262G CARBS\r\n15G BCAA\r\n9G LEUCINE',60.00,4,0,0.00,'2024-08-22 23:50:57','2025-03-22 17:25:33'),(37,'SERIOUS MASS ON (5.4kg)','Supports muscle building & weight gain\r\nHelps fuel intense workouts\r\n1250-1260 calories per serving\r\n50g protein per serving\r\n250-253 carbs per serving\r\n5g of creatine monohydrate per serving',90.00,4,1,11.00,'2024-08-23 00:37:08','2025-04-28 16:43:41'),(39,'MassTech Extreme 2000 (5.4kg)','MuscleTech Mass Gainer Protein Powder, Mass-Tech Extreme 2000, Muscle Builder Whey Protein Powder, Protein + Creatine + Carbs, Max-Protein Weight Gainer for Women & Men, Triple Chocolate.\r\n\r\nAbout this item\r\nMASS GAINER PROTEIN POWDER – Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 is a 5-in-1 hardcore mass gainer designed for individuals looking to put on extreme mass. Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 has everything you need to bulk up, pack on muscle and smash through strength plateaus\r\nProduct Note: Exposure to heat or sunlight may lead to melting/damage of product. Hence customers are expected to be available during the product delivery\r\nMUSCLE BUILDER – Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 delivers more protein per serving than most other mass gainers. With a whopping 80g of premium protein, your body will have all the building blocks it needs to build the size and muscle you’re looking for\r\nSUPERIOR WEIGHT GAINER – It’s clean and simple. Delivers more protein (80g), better calories and bigger results than other mass gainers, with the macros you need to pack on quality mass\r\nCREATINE MONOHYDRATE – Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 contains a clinically validated 10g dose of creatine monohydrate to help you increase strength and regenerate ATP stores that are reduced during resistance training\r\n   Report an issue with this product or seller\r\nNote: Products with electrical plugs are designed for use in the US. Outlets and voltage differ internationally and this product may require an adapter or converter for use in your destination. Please check compatibility before purchasing.',70.00,4,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 00:43:57','2025-05-26 20:33:03'),(40,'BULK MUSCLE XL (5.9kg)','BPI MASS GAINER : is an anabolic mass gainer that helps you build lean muscle with more protein, more muscle-building carbohydrates and more “good” calories per serving – so you can get thicker, bigger and stronger.\r\n\r\nBPI Sports Mass Gainer is a form of protein powder with higher calorie content than your regular whey protein. Bulk Muscle XL is unique in that it contains the finest protein available, without the excess fats that are in many other weight gainer formulas.\r\n\r\nOur high-quality protein powder mixes effortlessly with a blender, shaker or spoon for a smooth, easy-to-drink shake, every time.\r\n\r\nINSTRUCTIONS\r\nTake 1 serving (2 scoops) mixed in 350 ml of water after workouts or as a meal replacement.\r\n\r\nSupplement Facts\r\nServing Size = 2 Scoops\r\nServings per Container: 50',65.00,4,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 01:02:58','2024-08-23 01:55:45'),(41,'Challenger Nutrition - Thunder Gain (7.2kg)','SHORT DESCRIPTION\r\nThunder Gain is a great weight gainer available today for developing your physique to the fullest.\r\n\r\nDESCRIPTION\r\nFor serious athletes and bodybuilders, there’s a right way and a wrong way to gain weight. Thunder Gain weight gainer product will help you put on pounds in a healthy, efficient, and delicious way.\r\n\r\nThunder Gain contains pure whey protein concentrate and packs a punch with 1,250 calories per 334-gram serving. You’ll also get 50 full grams of protein and essential nutrients with each dose, including calcium, iron, and potassium.\r\n\r\nWe’ve designed this weight gainer for hardcore individuals looking to increase size and build strength faster. This high-calorie protein plus carbohydrate powder maximizes muscle mass while supplying energy to support muscle building. It also mixes well, is easy to digest, and has a delicious flavors taste.\r\n\r\nTrue challengers don’t accept anything less than the best. Thunder Gain is a great weight gainer available today for developing your physique to the fullest.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS\r\nContains ingredients from milk, soy, and coconut. Made in a facility that also processed sesame, egg, peanuts, tree nuts, fish, shellfish oils and wheat products.\r\n\r\nHOW TO USE\r\n1- Mix one Serving (4 scoops) with 750 ml of Thunder Gain with cold water or skimmed milk in shaker, or blender.\r\n\r\n2- Use between major meals. Thunder Gain is highly concentrated, due to its potency, you may want to consider using ½ serving two to three times a day.',75.00,4,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 01:07:07','2025-04-02 17:45:23'),(42,'Inner Armour Hard Mass Gainer (5.4kg)','Inner Armour Hard Mass Gainer 5lb Chocolate is a dietary supplement, which can help you gain extra calories and nutrients without adding to your fat. Thus, it can work wonders by helping you in gaining weight, and at the same time building your muscles and strength. Formulated with carbohydrates, protein, creatine and essential nutrients, this supplement can be taken in the form of shake after your workout sessions. It is also enhanced with amino acids that support muscle function and reduce muscle breakdown. Thus, it not only helps in the development of your muscles but also protects your hard-gained muscle mass. It minimises muscles fatigue and soreness.\r\n\r\n50g Protein\r\n267g Carbohydrates\r\n4g Creatine\r\n1277 Calories\r\n9g BCAAs andamp; Glutamine',60.00,4,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 01:31:10','2025-05-22 16:49:28'),(43,'Inner Armour Hard Mass Gainer (2.7kg)','Inner Armour Hard Mass Gainer 5lb Chocolate is a dietary supplement, which can help you gain extra calories and nutrients without adding to your fat. Thus, it can work wonders by helping you in gaining weight, and at the same time building your muscles and strength. Formulated with carbohydrates, protein, creatine and essential nutrients, this supplement can be taken in the form of shake after your workout sessions. It is also enhanced with amino acids that support muscle function and reduce muscle breakdown. Thus, it not only helps in the development of your muscles but also protects your hard-gained muscle mass. It minimises muscles fatigue and soreness.\r\n\r\n50g Protein\r\n267g Carbohydrates\r\n4g Creatine\r\n1277 Calories\r\n9g BCAAs andamp; Glutamine',35.00,4,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 01:37:04','2025-02-07 18:20:35'),(44,'Inner Armour ANABOLIC PEAK Gainer (2.7KG)','Inner Armour Hard Mass Gainer 5lb Chocolate is a dietary supplement, which can help you gain extra calories and nutrients without adding to your fat. Thus, it can work wonders by helping you in gaining weight, and at the same time building your muscles and strength. Formulated with carbohydrates, protein, creatine and essential nutrients, this supplement can be taken in the form of shake after your workout sessions. It is also enhanced with amino acids that support muscle function and reduce muscle breakdown. Thus, it not only helps in the development of your muscles but also protects your hard-gained muscle mass. It minimises muscles fatigue and soreness.\r\n\r\n50g Protein\r\n267g Carbohydrates\r\n4g Creatine\r\n1277 Calories\r\n9g BCAAs andamp; Glutamine',35.00,4,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 01:46:18','2025-05-22 16:49:41'),(45,'TOTAL WAR (30 SERVINGS)','AWARD WINNING AND #1 SELLING PREWORKOUT FORMULA\r\nCOMPLETE PREWORKOUT SUPPLEMENT WITH A POWERFUL COMBINATION OF ENDURANCE, PUMP, ENERGY AND FOCUS FACTORS\r\n320MG CAFFEINE FOR LONG LASTING ENERGY POWER YOUR TOUGHEST WORKOUTS\r\n6G L-CITRULLINE FOR ENHANCED BLOOD FLOW AND INTENSE PUMPS\r\n3.2G BETA ALANINE FOR MUSCULAR ENDURANCE AND PERFORMANCE\r\nFULLY TRANSPARENT LABEL SO YOU KNOW WHAT’S IN EVERY SCOOP OF YOUR PRE WORKOUT POWDER',25.00,9,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 03:31:28','2024-08-31 16:33:34'),(46,'Kevin Levrone Signature Series Shaboom Pump','Shaaboom Ice Pump. Food supplement. With sweeteners. Contains caffeine (200 mg / portion 9,25 g; 400 mg / daily portion 18,5 g). Not recommended for children or pregnant women. Pre-workout formula containing citrulline malate, beta-alanine and betaine intended for physically active adults.\r\n\r\nIngredients: citrulline malate, beta-alanine, L-arginine alphaketoglutarate (A-AKG), betaine anhydrous, stabiliser (glyceryl monostearate), acidity regulator (E500(ii)), anti-caking agent (E551), flavourings, caffeine anhydrous, salt, red beet juice concentrate1,2,3,5, black carrot concentrate5, sweeteners (acesulfame K, sucralose, steviol glycosides from Stevia), colour/s [(E160a)1,4,6, (E110)4]. E110: may have an adverse effect on activity and attention in children.\r\n\r\nRecommended use: Mix ~2 scoops of powder (9,25 g) with 150-175 ml of water. Drink 1 portion in the morning and 1 portion 30-45 minutes before workout.\r\n\r\nWarnings: Do not use if you are allergic to any of the product compounds. Do not exceed the recommended daily dose. Food supplements should not be used as a substitute for a varied diet. A varied and balanced diet and healthy lifestyle are recommended. Do not use if pregnant or nursing. Keep out of reach of young children. Do not exceed a dose of 400 mg caffeine per day from all sources. Do not consume with alcohol. If you take medications, you should consult your doctor before you consume the product. The measure included in the packet serves to facilitate portioning, but it does not guarantee precise dosing. It is advisable to use scales in order to measure out the exact amount. Shake the package well before use. This product is sold by weight not volume. Some settling of powder may occur during shipping and handling, which may affect density of powder. This product contains the serving indicated when measured exactly by weight.\r\n\r\nFlavours: Icy citrus-peach1, Icy dragon fruit2, Icy lychee3, Icy mango-passion fruit4, Icy blackberry-pineapple5, Icy orange-mango6.\r\n\r\nShaaboom Ice Pump. Food supplement\r\n\r\nServing size: ~1 Scoop (9,25 g)\r\nServings per container: 50\r\nAmount in	9,25 g	18,5 g\r\nCitrulline malate	3000 mg	6000 mg\r\n   of which citrulline	2000 mg	4000 mg\r\nBeta-alanine	1600 mg	3200 mg\r\nL-arginine alphaketoglutarate (A-AKG)	1000 mg	2000 mg\r\n   of which L-arginine	700 mg	1400 mg\r\nBetaine	750 mg	1500 mg\r\nGlyceryl monostearate	750 mg	1500 mg\r\nCaffeine	200 mg	400 mg',30.00,9,0,14.00,'2024-08-23 03:41:54','2024-09-12 20:46:42'),(47,'Pump 3G Zero Stim - Caffeine Free Pre-Workout 375g','Pump 3G 375g\r\nPRE-WORKOUT • NEXT GENERATION\r\n375G | 50 SCOOPS\r\n5G CITRULLINE | 3G AAKG | 3G CREATINE | 2G BETA-ALANINE\r\nPump 3G Next Generation now more concentrated than ever, stacked with a host of the most popular and researched ingredients to help improve pump, focus, and performance. Pump 3G was formulated whilst having the PUMP FACTOR prioritized at all stages of development in order to maximize gains, whilst still maintaining a potent stimulant dose.\r\n\r\nKEY BENEFITS\r\nCaffeine contributes to an increase in endurance capacity\r\nCreatine Monohydrate increases physical performance in successive bursts of short-term, high-intensity exercise\r\nVitamin B12 contributes to the reduction of tiredness and fatigue\r\nTested for Athletes\r\nHalal Certified Product\r\nDIRECTIONS FOR USE\r\nSUGGESTED USE\r\nMix 1 serving 15g (2 scoops) with 200ml of cold water 30 minutes prior to exercise and consume immediately.\r\n*Scoops are estimated only, weighing scales are recommended.',35.00,9,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 03:49:56','2025-02-10 20:36:49'),(50,'Applied Nutrition ABE: Ultimate Pre-Workout Formula 375g','30 SEEVINGS  take 1 scoop before 15 min of training.',25.00,9,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 04:09:04','2025-05-21 19:58:14'),(51,'C4 original pre-work out (30 servings)','C4 Original Pre Workout Powder - Vitamin C for Immune Support - Sugar Free Pre-workout Energy for Men & Women - 150mg Caffeine + Beta Alanine + Creatine +Arginine  - 30 Servings',25.00,9,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 21:29:21','2025-05-27 14:46:30'),(52,'BIOTECH USA Black Blood Pre-Work out (40 servings)','Sugar-free, extreme pre-workout food supplement drink powder with 400 mg caffeine, amino acids, vitamins, minerals and sweeteners.',35.00,9,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 21:36:44','2025-02-10 20:37:25'),(53,'API BCAA TRAINER (45 SERVINGS)','THE BENEFITS\r\nMEGA MUSCLE FOOD\r\nBy fueling muscle recovery and growth, BCAAs have been proven to help strength, physique, and endurance athletes train longer and harder. Maintain a leaner body, and prevent muscle breakdown with this cutting edge blend of citrulline and other high-quality ingredients. Make BCAA TRAINER your pre-workout and workout training partner.\r\n\r\nHIGH-TECH HYDRATION\r\nAPI’s BCAA TRAINER with hydration complex is a perfectly balanced blend of the branched chain amino acids (BCAAs) L-Leucine, L-Isoleucine and L-Valine. Explosive nitric oxide producing amino acid citrulline and electrolytes complete the chain of complex ingredients to keep you hydrated.\r\n\r\nBLOOD FLOW BOOST\r\nCitrulline in the ultra-refreshing BCAA TRAINER is converted into arginine in the body to increase blood flow, vascularity and nitric oxide production. It’s an extra energy equation that delivers massive pumps and fights training fatigue.\r\n\r\nHOW TO TAKE BCAA TRAINER\r\nMix 1 level scoop (8.6 grams) with 8-10 oz of water.\r\n\r\n.',30.00,8,1,22.20,'2024-08-23 21:50:06','2025-05-21 20:01:26'),(54,'RSP Fast Fuel (BCAA + CAFFINE) 30 servings','RSP Nutrition Fast Fuel is an elite pre-workout formula that provides clean energy, and optimizes endurance, hydration and muscle recovery. Each serving of Fast Fuel contains 250mg of natural caffeine, 5g of essential amino acids, 6 different electrolytes, 1000mg of Beta-Alanine & Creatine, and 500mg of L-Arginine.  These ingredients work together to boost your performance, help you push your limits, and crush your goals. Fast Fuel flavors are inspired by iconic destinations around the world where you can find RSP.',25.00,8,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 22:18:42','2025-03-05 18:53:05'),(55,'BPI BEST BCAA (30 servings)','Branch Chain Amino Acids, or BCAA\'s are an essential nutrient. Our bodies use them to for energy, and for maintaining muscle. \r\n\r\nBest BCAA is designed to give your body a boost when it needs it most. Used Intra-Workout or Post-Workout, our formula aims to facilitate fat loss, aid in muscle growth and recovery, and ignite muscle protein synthesis. Your body doesn\'t produce BCAAs naturally so Best BCAA is here to give you that boost!\r\n\r\nDelicious Flavors\r\nRecovery Aid\r\nIndustry Mixability .',25.00,8,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 22:28:38','2025-03-05 18:53:39'),(56,'BPI BEST BCAA (60 servings)','Branch Chain Amino Acids, or BCAA\'s are an essential nutrient. Our bodies use them to for energy, and for maintaining muscle. \r\n\r\nBest BCAA is designed to give your body a boost when it needs it most. Used Intra-Workout or Post-Workout, our formula aims to facilitate fat loss, aid in muscle growth and recovery, and ignite muscle protein synthesis. Your body doesn\'t produce BCAAs naturally so Best BCAA is here to give you that boost!\r\n\r\nDelicious Flavors\r\nRecovery Aid\r\nIndustry Mixability .',35.00,8,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 22:41:58','2025-05-22 16:59:09'),(57,'XTEND BCAA ( 30 SERVINGS )','XTEND Original is the BCAA that started it all. With it\'s huge selection of mouth-watering flavors, XTEND Original was designed to help you hydrate, repair, and recover.',25.00,8,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 22:53:33','2025-05-21 20:02:49'),(58,'VS BCAA PRO (26 SERVINGS)','BCAA PRO powered with 5g of BCAA as well as 5g of Glutamine at the same high dosage level to make you benefit from two essentials supplements merged in only one. In its unique formula BCAA PRO will keep your body machine in anabolic state essential for faster muscle tissue regeneration.\r\n\r\nCategory: STRENGTH UP\r\nTag: STRENGTH UP PRO LINE\r\n Description Nutrition Facts HOW TO TAKE! Barcodes \r\n/// BCAA PRO DEFINITION\r\nFaster recovery is the key to better achievements, V-SHAPE BCAA PRO powered with 5g of BCAA as well as 5g of Glutamine is the right supplement you certainly deserve!\r\n\r\nOnly the quickest possible muscle regeneration can stop catabolism and ensure the maximum muscle mass growth. If you are looking for an effective solution for quicker regeneration, V-SHAPE BCAA PRO will meet all your expectations and will help you to achieve any training goal!\r\n\r\nBCAA PRO 2in1 RECOVERY FORMULA!\r\nThe formula designed with a combination of top quality branched-chain amino acids (BCAAs) with potent ratio of 2:1:1 (leucine, isoleucine, valine) and instant glutamine form that will quickly make you notice the effect.\r\n\r\nYou will take maximum advantage of this muscle GAIN/RECOVERY in 1:1 ratio formula.\r\nRarely are the formulation combining both BCAA and Glutamine at the same high dosage level to make you benefit from two essentials supplements combined in only one!\r\nUnique, market-leading formula of branched-chain amino acids and glutamine lets you quickly and effectively replenish amino acids needed for proper functioning of every sportsman’s body.\r\n\r\nBCAA BENEFITS\r\nUnder heavy load the body demands large amounts of BCAAs. However, diet itself usually is not enough for sufficient supply of BCAA complex.\r\nBCAAs, namely L-leucine, L-valine and L-isoleucine are some of the amino acids metabolized directly in the muscles and are the only amino acids that exhibit the ability of stimulating the muscle protein synthesis independently. Thus, they help to block harmful catabolic reactions and contribute to better muscle mass gains. Additionally, BCAAs protect the muscle tissue and let you burn fat tissue faster, which is an enormously important aspect of supplementation when aiming of achieving a perfectly shaped body.\r\n\r\nGLUTAMINE ADVANTAGES\r\nGlutamine is also a key amino acid for the bodies of those who are physically active. As opposed to BCAA, glutamine belongs to the group of endogenous (produced in our body) amino acids, but it’s extremely difficult to ensure its sufficient supply relying only on a varied diet.\r\nGlutamine is badly needed to be supplemented to ensure the faster and maximum muscle recovery necessary to every hard trainer.\r\n\r\n \r\nRelated products\r\n\r\nMicronized Ultra-Filtered GLUTAMINE\r\n\r\nAMINO 10,000\r\n\r\nAAKG Strong\r\n\r\nv-itamin',25.00,8,1,0.00,'2024-08-23 23:01:11','2024-08-23 23:01:11'),(59,'Warrior Omega3 (60 servings)','Warrior Omega\r\nWarrior Omega Fish Oils 1000mg ensures you consume fats that are essential to maintaining a healthy system. The typical western lifestyle means we often lack in these essential fatty acids due to the typical \"western diet\" which tends to be high in processed foods, rather than omega rich sources such as oily fish and nuts.\r\n\r\nBenefits of Omega 3 Essential Fatty Acids\r\nSupplementation with Warrior Omega can help to boost your intake levels of these essential nutrients, and a healthy intake of Omega 3 Essential Fatty acids may help to:\r\n\r\nMaintain healthy skin, hair, teeth and gums\r\nMaintain healthy bones and joints\r\nSupport a healthy immune system\r\nMaintain a healthy cardiovascular system\r\nMaintain normal mood and a healthy nervous system',10.00,11,0,0.00,'2024-08-23 23:19:49','2025-02-10 20:38:31'),(60,'ALLMAX OMEGA3','OMEGA3\r\nSource of Omega 3 Essential Fatty Acids (EFA)\r\nExcellent Source of EPA180mg and DHA120mg\r\nHelps Support Brain Function and Heart Health',25.00,11,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 00:12:11','2025-05-22 17:02:12'),(61,'MUSCLETECH 100% FISH OIL','Platinum 100% Omega Fish Oil100 soft gel delivers ultra-pure fish oils, which are an excellent source of the omega-3 fatty acids docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA). Fish oils help speed up recovery time, burn body fat and promote muscle growth.',15.00,11,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 00:17:11','2025-05-08 16:56:37'),(62,'MUSCLTECH MULTI VITAMIN (90 tablets)','A complete, advanced multivitamin complex packed with high-potency vitamins and minerals, plus an amino support matrix',20.00,11,1,0.00,'2024-08-24 00:35:19','2025-02-28 16:13:46'),(63,'USN Z-MAG+ (180 CAPSULE)','Performance Z-Mag+ supports strength, recovery, and endurance gains.  Z-Mag+ is a combination of Zinc, Magnesium, and Vitamin B6.\r\n\r\n30mg Zinc per serving\r\n450mg Magnesium per serving\r\n10.5mg Vitamin B6 per serving',25.00,11,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 00:45:10','2025-02-10 20:39:33'),(64,'BIOTECH USA DAILY PACK (30 packs)','Food supplement pills and capsules, containing vitamins, minerals, omega-3, lecithin and plant extracts.',45.00,11,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 00:59:23','2025-02-10 20:39:50'),(65,'Hepaplus Liver & digestion (30 capsule)','Hepaplus™ is a complex composition of artichoke extract (Cynara scolymus L.) standardized to 5% content of cynarine, which supports the proper functioning of the liver and digestive system. The formula has been enriched with L-ornithine aspartate and group B vitamins B1, B2, B6, niacin and pantothenic acid, which participate in proper energy metabolism.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nNutritional information\r\n1 capsule\r\nCynara extract (Cynara scolymus L.) standardised to 5% cinarine\r\n350 mg\r\nL-ornithine aspartate\r\n100 mg\r\nThiamine (vit. B1)\r\n0,55 mg (50%*)\r\nRiboflavin (vit. B2)\r\n0,7 mg (50%*)\r\nNiacin (vit. B3)\r\n8 mg (50%*)\r\nPantothenic acid (vit. B5)\r\n3 mg (50%*)\r\nVitamin B6\r\n0,7 mg (50%*)',13.00,11,1,0.00,'2024-08-24 01:05:50','2024-08-24 01:05:50'),(74,'Muscletech Cell Tech (27 servings)','Cell-Tech is the best for a reason. Specifically formulated for those looking to pack on lean muscle, Cell-Tech is scientifically engineered, third-generation creatine formula featuring a clinically validated blend of creatine monohydrate and carbohydrates. For more that two decades, Cell-Tech has helped athletes who have trouble putting on size make unprecedented gains. It\'s grown to become a legendary staple in the supplement regimen of serious competitors – and proof that MuscleTech continues to push the limits of science and research everyday.\r\nFaster muscle growth\r\n\r\nProven to enhance strength & performance\r\n\r\nImprove recovery',35.00,3,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 01:13:13','2025-03-08 15:46:56'),(75,'Muscletech Cell Tech (54 servings)','Creatine:10G / Aminos:5G / ALA:200MG / SERVINGS:54\r\n\r\nCell-Tech is the best for a reason. Specifically formulated for those looking to pack on lean muscle, Cell-Tech is scientifically engineered, third-generation creatine formula featuring a clinically validated blend of creatine monohydrate and carbohydrates. For more that two decades, Cell-Tech has helped athletes who have trouble putting on size make unprecedented gains. It\'s grown to become a legendary staple in the supplement regimen of serious competitors – and proof that MuscleTech continues to push the limits of science and research everyday.\r\nFaster muscle growth\r\n\r\nProven to enhance strength & performance\r\n\r\nImprove recovery',55.00,3,1,10.00,'2024-08-24 01:24:44','2024-08-24 01:24:44'),(76,'Victory Martinez Glutamine (60 servings)','L-Glutamine is the most abundant Amino Acid in the human body. Amazingly, around 60 percent of your skeletal muscle is made up of Glutamine, and your body uses and depletes it rapidly - especially in active individuals who workout or play sports. As an Essential Amino Acid, Glutamine is critical in minimizing muscle breakdown, supporting endurance, helping gut function and enhancing nutrient absorption.\r\n\r\nBenefits of Glutamine Supplementation:\r\n\r\n- Can Accelerate Recovery Times & Reduce Soreness\r\n\r\n- May Restore Immune System Health\r\n\r\n- Supports Improved Digestive Health\r\n\r\n- May Help Improve Strength Gains\r\n\r\n- Has Been Shown To Improve Hydration',25.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 01:40:50','2025-03-05 18:52:00'),(78,'MEGA SPORT AMINO HARDCORE (325 TABLETS)','Amino acids are the building blocks of proteins and muscle tissue. All types of physiological processes relating to sport – energy, recovery, muscle / strength gains and fat loss, as well as mood and brain function – are intimately and critically linked to amino acids. It is no wonder amino acids have become major players in athletes supplementation, especially among bodybuilders. Amino hardcore is a powerful blend of all three Branched Chained Amino Acids plus other essential aminos. Scientifically formulated with high bioavailability for your hardcore bodybuilding regimen, Amino Hardcore provides crucial building blocks for protein, which is the main component of muscle tissue.\r\n\r\nIngrediants\r\nServings Per Container: 54	Amount Per Serving % DV*	\r\nCalories	90	\r\nCalories From Fat	18	\r\nTotal Fat	2g	1.5%\r\nCalcium	34mg	2%\r\nSodium	20mg	< 1%\r\nProtein	12,000mg	24%\r\nof which saturates	0.06 g	0.1 g\r\nDietary fiber	0.4 g	0.5 g\r\nSodium	0.4 g	0.6 g\r\nL-Glutamic Acid	2440mg	*\r\nL-Proline	1240mg	*\r\nGlycine	280mg	*\r\nL-Leucine (BCAA)	1000mg	*\r\nL-Lysine	880mg	*\r\nAspartic acid	760mg	*\r\nL-Alanine	320mg	*\r\nL-Arginine	480mg	*\r\nL-Valine (BCAA)	760mg	*\r\nL-Serine	680mg	*\r\nL-Phenylalanine	520mg	*\r\nL-Isoleucine (BCAA)	640mg	*\r\nL-Tyrosine	680mg	*\r\nL-Threonin	520mg	*\r\nL-Histidine	320mg	*\r\nL-Methionine	420mg	*\r\nL-Tryptophan**	120mg	*\r\nL-Cystine	40mg	*',30.00,6,1,0.00,'2024-08-24 01:52:00','2025-02-28 16:13:03'),(79,'RED REX EAA + CREATINE HCL (30 SERVINGS)','EAA + Creatine HCL is a full spectrum EAA profile consisting of all 9 Essential Amino Acids and muscle building Creatine HCL. Each serving delivers 6G\'s of BCAAs making this a superior, advanced recovery, intra and post workout product compared to the stand alone BCAA supplement.\r\n\r\nResearched Proven 2:1:1 Ratio Of BCAAs: Branch Chain Amino Acids Leucine, Isoleucine and Valine supports helps prevent muscle breakdown during workouts, muscle repair and aids in post-workout recovery.\r\n\r\nLean Muscle Growth: When taken intra-workout or post-workout, EAAs have been shown to increase muscle protein synthesis, leading to better gains in lean muscle growth and recovery. \r\n\r\nBenefits of Creatine HCL:\r\n\r\nRequires a lower dose than Creatine Monohydrate\r\nDoes not require a “loading cycle” \r\nFaster absorption\r\nIncreased body mass\r\nFaster muscle recovery\r\nReduced fatigue\r\nRelatively faster gains in strength',30.00,8,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 02:01:59','2025-04-15 14:34:50'),(80,'Carnivor Beef Amino (300 Tablets)','Carnivor Beef Aminos - Tablets\r\nMuscleMeds Ultra-Concentrated CARNIVOR 100% BEEF AMINOS use a patented processing technology to provide high concentrations of quality amino acids. Made from the finest premium grade Beef Protein Isolate, Beef Albumin, Argentinian Desiccated Beef Liver and Beef Immunoglobulin, each ultra-concentrated tablet provides a full spectrum of essential amino acids including high levels of Branched Chain Amino Acids (BCAAs) and bio-active growth factors. Plus, the addition of creatine helps increase muscle size and strength, while added Branched Chain Keto Acids (BCKAs) help you recycle these concentrated amino acids for enhanced nitrogen retention. This powerful amino acid formula will allow you to harness the muscle building force of beef without any fat or cholesterol, and with even higher concentrations of aminos, creatine and growth factors!',25.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-08-24 02:10:55','2024-09-12 20:39:45'),(86,'Bcaa + Creatine','Bcaa 30 servings + Creatine 60 servings',30.00,5,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 17:18:00','2025-04-19 20:20:11'),(89,'MUSCLTECH TEST HD (90 CAPLETS)','Take 1 serving (1 caplet) twice daily. Take the first caplet in the morning and the second caplet in the midafternoon. On workout days, take the second serving 30 minutes before your workout. Do not exceed 2 servings in a 24-hour period. Read the entire label before use and follow the directions provided.',28.00,7,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 19:47:16','2025-04-15 14:35:30'),(90,'ANABOL HARDCORE (60 LIQUI-CAPS)','ACTIVATE REAL ANABOLISM FOR BIGGER, STRONGER, HARDER AND DENSER MUSCLES: A a powerful ANABOLIC ACTIVATOR. It is for those who want to build lean, dense, high-quality muscles with extra hardness.\r\nTRIGGER MUSCLE PROTEIN SYNTHESIS: When used in combination with intense weight training, and muscle building exercises and sports activities. The adaptogenic properties of ANABOL help signal your body to increase muscle protein synthesis. muscle-building, recovery and strength gains can occur at a faster pace. You should consume a high protein diet while taking ANABOL.\r\nVEGETARIAN FRIENDLY: Made with fast absorbing vegetable caps and free of animal products. This can safely be used with a vegetarian diet.\r\nACHIEVE LEANER AND DENSER MUSCLE MASS: Perfect for bodybuilding, weight lifting, and athletes who need increased strength.\r\nREPAIR MUSCLE & RECOVER FASTER: Not only does it help build muscle, it makes your recovery time faster.',30.00,7,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 19:52:55','2024-08-27 19:52:55'),(91,'UNIVERSAL GH MAX (180 TABLETS)','Growth hormone (GH) can add lean mass by stimulating protein synthesis and increasing nitrogen retention in muscles. Universal Nutrition’s GH Max is the ultimate GH support formula. It is designed for the elite strength athlete who is interested in optimizing strength and power. GH Max is enhanced with arginine and ornithine, along with other anabolic support nutrients, to help you reach your strength goals.',40.00,7,1,12.50,'2024-08-27 20:03:21','2024-08-27 20:03:21'),(92,'RC TRIBULUS XS (120 CAPSULES)','As a dietary supplement, take 1-2 capsules daily, preferably with morning and evening meals and with plenty of water. Use in conjunction with a proper diet and exercise regimen.\r\n500mg Tribulus  per serving\r\n120 servings per container\r\nDesigned to increase endurance*\r\nZero added fillers or stimulants',28.00,7,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 20:11:40','2024-09-12 20:44:26'),(93,'TRIBU 2000 (90 TABLETS)','Scitec Nutrition Tribu 2000 is a nutritional supplement containing Tribulus terrestris extract. One tablet contains up to 2000 mg of an extract with a high content of saponins.\r\nAccording to current EU legislation, we may not include more detailed information on herbs and herbal products that could give the impression of a health or healing effect of the herbs. Likewise, we are not allowed to mention the effects of herbs proven by scientific research and studies, unless it is a medicine registered by a pharmaceutical company.\r\nBenefits\r\nup to 2000 mg of Tribulus terrestris extract per tablet\r\nhigh content of saponins\r\nDirections of use\r\nTake 1 tablet a day with a glass of water.',30.00,7,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 20:16:20','2024-08-27 20:29:12'),(95,'ASHWAGANDHA NOW (90 VEG CAPSULES)','Ayurvedic adaptogen: Ashwagandha is used as a general tonic and adaptogen, helping the body adapt to temporary normal stress. Now Ashwagandha is a standardized extract (450 milligrams per serving). Take 1 capsule 2 to 3 times daily.\r\nFree radical scavenger/Immune system support: Preliminary data suggest that Ashwagandha supports a healthy immune system.\r\nCertifications/classifications: Non-GMO, kosher, dairy free, egg free, nut free, soy free, vegan/vegetarian, made without gluten\r\nGMP quality assured: NPA A-rated GMP certification means that every aspect of the NOW manufacturing process has been examined, including our laboratory/testing methods (for stability, potency, and product formulation).',25.00,10,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 20:46:53','2025-04-08 16:50:47'),(96,'ASHWAGANDHA ROOT 920 MG (90 CAPSULES)','What Is Ashwagandha?\r\n\r\nAshwagandha is a traditional herb that has been used in Ayurvedic wellness practices for centuries. Derived from the roots of the Withania somnifera plant, it is a member of the nightshade family and is native to India and Asia. Many people seek ashwagandha root supplements as the roots are touted for being high in naturally occurring antioxidants.\r\n\r\nNature’s Truth Ashwagandha Root Capsules\r\n\r\nThese capsules feature ashwagandha derived directly from the root of Withania somnifera, delivering the equivalent of 920 mg of concentrated Ashwagandha Root extract in every serving.** Two quick release capsules provide a high-quality source of this traditional herb and are easy to integrate into your daily routine.\r\n\r\nNature’s Truth: Where Wellness Begins\r\n\r\nOur mission at Nature’s Truth is to meet your wellness needs with products that go above and beyond. Nature’s Truth provides supplements in various delivery forms, such as capsules, softgels, chewables, tablets, powders, liquids, and gummies to suit every preference. Our Ashwagandha Root is non-GMO and free of gluten, wheat, yeast, milk, lactose, soy, artificial color, artificial flavor, artificial sweetener, and preservatives.',25.00,10,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 20:50:55','2025-05-07 20:09:53'),(97,'MACA 525 MG','Maca root is a vegetable native to Peru where it\'s used as both a food source and for medicinal applications. Maca root has been shown to increase sexual desire, stamina and energy for improved sexual performance.',25.00,10,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 21:03:29','2025-04-08 16:50:58'),(98,'SCITEC ASHWAGANDHA 226 MG (60 CAPSULES)','Ashwagandha\r\n226 mg Ashwagandha root extract\r\n60 daily dose\r\nThe herbal ingredients have been used by mankind for a long time, for various purposes, and can be considered part of folk traditions. The importance of extracts lies in the fact that they do not focus on the whole plant, but on the extraction of its biologically active components, its concentrated active ingredients, separated from the plant fibres. To do this, different technological solutions can be used, a process called extraction.\r\n\r\nThe product is named after Withania somnifera, better known as Ashwagandha, but also known as Indian ginseng. It is a long-established plant in Ayurveda*, and its active ingredient, lactones, can be used for a variety of purposes.\r\n\r\nWe recommend Ashwagandha:\r\n\r\nFor both women and men.\r\nNot just for athletes.\r\nFor those who are looking for an easy to dose, capsule product.\r\nFor those who are looking for a product that can be taken with a complex multivitamin.\r\nDIRECTIONS\r\nTake 1 capsule daily before meals with a glass of water.\r\n\r\nWARNINGS\r\nKeep out of reach of small children! This food supplement is not a substitute for a balanced, varied diet and a healthy lifestyle! Do not exceed the recommended daily intake!\r\nThe product is not recommended for pregnant women, nursing mothers or persons under 12 years of age. Consumption of the product is not recommended in case of known underlying diseases or when taking medication.',30.00,10,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 21:11:26','2025-04-15 14:41:36'),(99,'SOLARAY CHROMIUM (100 TABLETS)','The Chromium in Solaray Chromium Picolinate is trivalent chromium which is the most desired form. Solaray Chromium Picolinate is specially formulated to provide nutritive support for assisting the body in maintaining normal, healthy insulin action and glucose utilization. Solaray Chromium Picolinate is an advanced chromium supplement. Solaray Chromium Picolinate provides 200 mcg. of Chromium per serving. Chromium is an essential trace mineral that helps the body maintain normal blood sugar levels.',25.00,10,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 21:21:30','2025-04-08 16:51:10'),(100,'APPLE CIDER SLIM (24 TABLETS)','Helps with Weight Control, increases the metabolism rate\r\nBalances Blood Sugar Levels\r\nHelps with Cholesterol Levels\r\nAntimicrobial',10.00,10,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 21:38:18','2024-08-27 21:38:18'),(101,'SCITEC WATER CUT (100 CAPSULE)','Water Cut\r\nWith vitamin C and vitamin B6\r\nWith 6 types of plant extracts\r\n400 mg of green tea extract in the daily dose\r\n40 mg of caffeine per day\r\nThe Water Cut capsule contains two vitamins and 6 types of plant extracts. Its daily dose contains significant amounts of vitamin C and vitamin B6, 1250% of the daily intake reference value for the former and 580% for the latter. Vitamin C and vitamin B6 contribute to the reduction of tiredness and fatigue and to the normal functioning of the immune system. Vitamin C, also known as ascorbic acid, also contributes to the protection of cells against oxidative stress, and vitamin B6 to the regulation of hormonal activity.\r\n\r\nIn addition to vitamins, the product\'s ingredients include green tea, artichoke, cranberry, dandelion, parsley and common juniper extracts. Most of the polyphenolic compounds found in green tea are catechins, of which EGCG (epigallocatechin gallate) is one of the best known. The daily dose of the product contains 40 mg of caffeine, part of which comes from green tea extract and another part from added anhydrous caffeine.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the phenolic compounds of green tea, the active ingredient palette of the product includes proanthocyanidin from blueberries, flavonoid compounds from dandelion and cynarin from artichoke.\r\n\r\nDIRECTIONS\r\nTake 2x2 capsules with 500 ml of water.\r\n\r\nWARNINGS\r\nStore the product out of the reach of small children! Dietary supplements do not replace a balanced, varied diet and a healthy lifestyle. Do not exceed the recommended daily consumption amount! Do not consume on an empty stomach or before going to bed! Contains caffeine (40 mg/4 capsules). Pregnant and lactating women and children under 18 cannot consume it. Not recommended in case of known underlying disease and/or medication. Not recommended for people with cardiovascular diseases, high blood pressure and caffeine sensitivity. Contains 30 mg/serving (2 capsules) of EGCG [(-)-epigallocatechin-3-gallate]. It cannot be consumed on the same day as other products containing green tea. The daily consumption of EGCG should not reach or exceed 800 mg per day.\r\n\r\nSTORAGE\r\nStore tightly closed in a cool, dry place.',30.00,12,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:06:07','2025-03-04 15:14:41'),(102,'ANIMAL CUT (42 PACKS)','An award-winning supplement, Animal Cuts includes potent thermogenic fat burners that can help boost the body’s natural ability to burn stored body fat while promoting lean mass.\r\nIncludes 8 Research-Backed Complexes for Fat Loss and Cutting\r\n\r\nThermogenic and Metabolic Complexes\r\n\r\nBurn excess fat thermogenically and boost metabolism naturally\r\n\r\nNootropic and Cortisol - Inhibiting Complexes\r\n\r\nBrain boosters for better focus and increased alertness plus reduced stress with patented SerinAid\r\n\r\nDiuretic and Thyroid Support and Complexes\r\n\r\nCut fat and shed excess water weight without losing pump or muscle size naturally\r\n\r\nAppetite Suppressant and Bioavailability Complexes\r\n\r\nSuppresses appetite with CCK boosters plus a delivery system including patented Bioperine',45.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:11:18','2025-03-24 17:45:37'),(103,'LIPO 6 BLACK (60 BLACK-CAPS)','If you’re ready to take your weight loss to the next level - then LIPO-6 BLACK UC has your back. Designed as a potent fat-destroying formula - LIPO-6 BLACK UC harnesses the power of metabolism-boosting ingredients to help you shed those extra pounds. By converting stored fat into energy - this supplement ensures you have the stamina to power through your workouts while simultaneously burning calories. Utilizing cutting-edge liquid-cap technology - LIPO-6 BLACK UC guarantees rapid absorption of its powerful components so you can see rapid results. However, LIPO-6 BLACK UC goes beyond just fat burning as it helps curb food cravings - preventing overeating so you stay on track with your diet. See the power of LIPO-6 BLACK UC',20.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:23:31','2025-04-21 18:59:13'),(104,'LIPO 6 BLACK INTENSE (60 BLACK-CAPS)','Ignite your fat loss with the EXTREME fat burner - LIPO-6 INTENSE UC. This powerhouse product is designed for those who are serious about conquering stubborn fat. LIPO-6 INTENSE UC is an ultra-concentrated formula that delivers a surge of intense thermogenic heat that reignites your metabolism. Experience an intense boost in energy and focus - allowing you to blast through even the most brutal of workout sessions. Take your fat burning to the extreme',25.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:27:59','2025-05-22 17:03:02'),(105,'LIPO 6 HARDCORE  (60 BLACK-CAPS)','LIPO-6 HARDCORE is a powerful thermogenic formula designed to help you lose fat while preserving muscle. It works by turning your body into a fat-burning furnace - so you can utilize it for energy while you\'re trying to get lean. Each pill offers an energy surge and enhanced appetite control - making it easier to stick to your diet. LIPO-6 HARDCORE is labeled as such for a reason - its potency is unmatched - so keeping to the recommended dosage is a must. If you’re looking to get in shape and lose fat without losing muscle',25.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:31:03','2024-08-27 22:31:03'),(106,'TURBO RIPPER (100 CAPSULES)','Description\r\nTURBO RIPPER\r\nSTRONG AND SISTAINED STIMULATION!\r\nHIGH DOSES OF SUSTAINED RELEASE CAFFEINE, ACETYL L-CARNITINE, GREEN TEA, SYNEPHRINE & MORE!\r\nTURBO RIPPER gives you many of the ingredients you know and love – in significant doses! We have L-Carnitine and not just ordinary L-Carnitine, but the more complex Acetyl L-Carnitine (ALC) in a whopping dose – you probably won’t want to take Carnitine separately!\r\n\r\n \r\nNor do you have to take any of the other ingredients TURBO RIPPER provides in one single serving: Catechin rich Green Tea extract; Tyrosine that is the precursor to many important hormones and neurotransmitters; or Bitter Orange extract standardized for Synephrine. Also, TURBO RIPPER gives you a serious Caffeine jolt of 200 milligrams per serving from various sources, including the trademarked NEWCAFF microencapsulated, sustained release Caffeine! It is a new Caffeine delivery system, which releases its total Caffeine content over approximately 4 hours.\r\n\r\nDirections\r\nStart with 1-2 caps 1-2 times a day to assess stimulant tolerance! A full serving is 4 capsules a day. Cycle usage: use for 8-12 weeks, then take at least 2 weeks of. Avoid any other sources of stimulants while using! This product provides a sustained release of Caffeine for approximately 4 hours after taking! Use this product in conjunction with food as part of a healthy, balanced diet, not as a substitute for such.',35.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:37:58','2024-08-27 22:37:58'),(107,'L-CARNITINE+TARTRATE (120 CAPSULES)','ALLMAX introduces L-Carnitine Capsules in the form of L-Carnitine L-Tartrate (LCLT), one of the world’s most bio-available forms of L-Carnitine supplementation. L-Carnitine is essential for transporting long-chain fats into the cell (mitochondria). L-Carnitine taps into your fat supply and may provide support to burn it as fuel, resulting in increased energy. Without L-Carnitine, these fats cannot be burned for energy and are instead shunted to stored body fat.',30.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:49:12','2025-04-11 18:58:40'),(108,'CLA 1000','DEFINITION\r\nWant a leaner physique? CLA 1000 packs a serious punch with its super-concentrated dose of naturally occurring Conjugated Linoleic Acid. This scientifically designed supplement is the go-to choice for those looking to cultivate leanness, muscle definition, and metabolic efficiency. The transformative effects of Conjugated Linoleic Acid are backed by research - secure your bottle of CLA 1000 today.',20.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-08-27 22:55:18','2024-08-27 22:55:18'),(109,'GLUTAMINE DRIVE (60 SERVINGS)','RECOVER. REBUILD. PROTECT YOUR GAINS\r\nGlutamine is a crucial nutrient for muscle growth - comprising 60% of muscle amino acids. This vital supply diminishes due to intense training, dieting and stress - leading to muscle breakdown. Supplementing with L-Glutamine maintains optimal levels - so your muscle growth and recovery are optimized. GLUTAMINE PURE offers pure, unflavored L-Glutamine that mixes easily into any beverage. Include it during your post-workout routine to accelerate muscle repair and prime them for faster growth.',18.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 23:01:17','2025-02-10 20:42:09'),(110,'CARBO XTREME (30 SERVINGS)','Get your carbs the healthy and efficient way with our energy-boosting Carbo Xtreme. Beyond the 49  grams of total carbohydrates, this is a source of well-balanced nutrition providing 200 calories, and 1 gram of sugar. It’s easy to digest, has  delicious flavors, and a pure fuel for your muscles before, during, and after training.',35.00,13,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 23:27:03','2025-02-10 20:42:15'),(111,'ORIGIN COLLAGEN (25 SERVINGS)','Collagen is often called the body’s scaffolding.  It’s the glue that holds the body together. Collagen is the most abundant source of protein in our body, but as we grow older our body’s natural production of it declines. Enter ORIGIN COLLAGEN!',30.00,15,0,0.00,'2024-08-27 23:52:26','2025-04-15 14:44:09'),(112,'L-ARGININE 1000MG (120 CAPSULES)','THE AMINO VASODIALATOR FOR INSANE PUMPS & PERFORMANCE\r\nLet L-ARGININE 1000 unlock your performance potential with the power of enhanced blood flow. A potent amino acid - L-Arginine acts as a vasodilator - converting seamlessly into Nitric Oxide within the body. The result? Amplified blood flow - leading to better muscle pumps, optimized workouts, and a boost in overall performance. Beyond muscle pumps - this supplement plays a pivotal role in supporting male performance',20.00,6,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 00:02:31','2025-05-26 20:42:06'),(113,'L-CITRULINE (90 SERVINGS)','CORE CHAMPS L-CITRULLINE 2000MG supports vasodilation through nitric oxide production, helping to improve blood flow and muscle pumps during a workout. L-Citrulline Malate is an amino acid that works to raise both arginine and ornithine plasma levels more efficiently and for longer periods.',25.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-08-28 00:06:29','2024-09-10 22:32:45'),(114,'INNER ARMOUR CREATINE (133 SERVINGS)','Micronized Creatine Monohydrate Powder - Increase Muscle Strength & Endurance - Fast Dissolving, Flavor-Free, Vegan Fitness Supplement, Keto Friendly - 400 gr or 133 Servings',20.00,3,0,0.00,'2024-08-28 00:09:46','2025-05-26 20:40:20'),(115,'BETA ALANINE (90 MEGA CAPSULES)','Key Features\r\nPure amino acid content \r\nMega Capsules packaging\r\nBeta-alanine is a prematerial of carnosine. The boosting of the carnosine level through supplements is increasingly more popular among well-informed athletes and bodybuilders. Carnosine is found in the skeletal muscles, primarily in type II, fast-twitching muscle fibres. \r\n\r\nThe larger capsules contain 10% more active ingredients.\r\n\r\n*Compared with the predecessor of the BioTechUSA Beta-Alanine capsule.\r\n\r\nWho is Beta-Alanine powder recommended to\r\nto those who do endurance sports, to be taken prior to workout \r\nbodybuilders\r\nLike all BioTech USA products, Beta-alanine powder consists of safe and carefully selected ingredients.\r\n\r\nRecommended use\r\nTake 4 capsules daily (1 capsule every 4 hours with a large glass of water). Do not exceed the recommended dosage.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS: Beta alanine (84%), capsule shell [gelatine, glazing agent (shellac), colour (iron oxides and hydroxides), acidity regulator (ammoni-um hydroxide), acidity regulator (potassium hydroxide)], anti-caking agents (magnesium salts of fatty acids, silicon dioxide). Made in a plant that manufactures milk, egg, gluten, soy, crustaceans, sulphur dioxide and nuts containing foods.\r\n\r\nActive substance table\r\n\r\n(daily dose: 4 capsules, number of daily doses in the product: 22.5)',25.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-08-28 00:23:34','2025-03-24 16:15:17'),(116,'LIVEPRO BETA-ALANINE PRO (100 SERVINGS)','BETA-ALANINE PRO. Food supplement. BETA-ALANINE PRO contains the highest quality beta-alanine. Ingredients: Beta-alanine. Recommended use: Mix 3 g of powder (~ ½ scoop) with 150-200 ml of water. Drink 30 minutes before exercise. The measure included in the packet serves to facilitate portioning, but it does not guarantee precise dosing. It is advisable to use scales in order to measure out the exact amount. Warnings: Do not use if you are allergic to any of the product compounds. Do not exceed the recommended daily dose. Food supplements should not be used as a substitute for a varied diet. Do not use if pregnant or nursing. A varied and balanced diet and healthy lifestyle are recommended. If you take medications, you should consult your doctor before you consume the product. Keep out of reach of young children',25.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-08-28 00:32:21','2025-03-24 16:15:09'),(117,'DOUBLE SHAKER','Double shaker 350 ml \r\n700 ml you can drink tow types of the supplement',8.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 22:00:22','2024-08-28 22:00:22'),(118,'SPIDER SHAKER','Spider shaker 500 ml \r\n- Blender ball with wire whisk as you shake \r\n-Perfect for protein shakes, smoothies\r\n-Dual storage container holds 2 servings \r\n-Extra pill container \r\n-Detachable parts to set up as per your convenience',6.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 22:14:46','2024-08-28 22:14:46'),(119,'REGULAR SHAKER','Regular shaker 600 ml \r\nNo water leaking from the bottle \r\nhigh quality shaker',4.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 22:38:16','2024-08-28 22:38:16'),(120,'BEAST REGULAR SHAKER','Regular shaker 600 ml \r\nNo water leaking from the bottle \r\nhigh quality shaker',5.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 22:46:36','2024-08-28 22:46:36'),(122,'REGULAR SHAKER','Regular shaker 600 ml \r\nNo water leaking from the bottle \r\nhigh quality shaker',4.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 23:08:52','2024-08-28 23:08:52'),(123,'REGULAR SHAKER','Regular shaker 600 ml \r\nNo water leaking from the bottle \r\nhigh quality shaker',4.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 23:10:39','2024-08-28 23:10:39'),(124,'PORTECLE','Protein Powder Container with Funnel - The Portable Protein Powder Container with Funnel & Belt Key Chain for Easy Carrying -100ml',5.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 23:17:55','2024-08-28 23:17:55'),(125,'MYPROTINE HOLDER SHAKER','Holder shaker \r\nyou can take 3 scoop of protein powder in side the same shaker',7.00,16,1,0.00,'2024-08-28 23:24:34','2024-08-28 23:24:34'),(131,'PLATINUM HYDROWHEY (40 SERVINGS)','30 Grams of Protein Per Serving\r\n8.8 Grams of Naturally Occurring & Added BCAAs per Serving\r\nMade with 100% Hydrolyzed Whey Protein Isolate\r\nHydrolyzed, Quick Digesting\r\nPLATINUM HYDROWHEY is the most advanced whey protein we’ve ever developed containing 100% Hydrolyzed Whey Protein Isolate. Hydrolyzed Whey Protein Isolate has much of the carbohydrates, fat and lactose ‘isolated’ out using sophisticated filtering technologies, and hydrolyzing breaks larger proteins down into smaller pieces, so ultra-pure whey isolate is able to get into your system rapidly for muscle recovery support. Finally, we dialed up this ultra-pure and rapidly digesting formula with added micronized Branched Chain Amino Acids (BCAAs).',90.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-09-02 21:44:30','2024-09-02 21:44:30'),(132,'CARNIVOR BEEF PROTEIN (56 SERVINGS)','CARNIVOR Beef Protein Isolate delivers all the muscle-building power of beef with greater amino acid levels than other protein sources used in supplements, including whey, soy, milk, and egg. CARNIVOR Beef Protein Isolate (BPI) is even 350% more concentrated in anabolic muscle building aminos than a prime sirloin steak! Plus, it is sugar-free, fat-free, lactose-free, and cholesterol-free! Not to mention, CARNIVOR is one of the most delicious protein shakes you’ll ever try!\r\n\r\nFACT: Nearly 70% of the global population is intolerant to lactose. Milk proteins such as whey and casein contain lactose and are poorly digested by most people, which can cause stomach distress and boating. Carnivor Beef Protein Isolate will resolve any gastric issues you are experiencing from whey and give you the quality protein you need to build muscle.',70.00,14,0,0.00,'2024-09-02 22:17:43','2025-04-15 14:41:18'),(133,'NUTREX LIQUID L-CARNITINE 3000 (31 SERVINGS)','Unlock the fat-burning power of an optimized metabolism and enhance your endurance with Liquid L-CARNITINE 3000. This formula is designed to maximize your body\'s ability to convert fat into energy using L-Carnitine – a renowned amino acid. L-Carnitine has been used by professionals for years to transform their physique - now it’s your turn. This research-backed formula is essential for those looking to take their bodies and performance to the next phase of their evolution - get your Liquid L-CARNITINE 3000 today.',25.00,12,0,0.00,'2024-09-02 22:28:24','2025-05-22 17:03:35'),(134,'CLA + Carnitine - Non-Stimulant Weight Loss Supplement','BURN. ENERGY. STIM-FREE.\r\nCLA+Carnitine is our solution to the fat burning market. Instead of loading you up with caffeine we use a science based thermogenic approach. Conjugated Linoleic Acid, or CLA, is a naturally occurring, healthy, omega-6 fatty acid that is found in some food. We cannot produce CLA on our own so supplementation can become necessary to get an efficacious dose. CLA has been shown in studies to stimulate fat loss and help the body convert fat to energy.\r\n\r\nCarnitine is an amino acid that is crucial to our functioning bodies. Carnitine is shown to help the body transport fatty acids to our cells to be used as energy. \r\n\r\nTogether CLA+Carnitine is a powerhouse in the fat burner space. Formulated to help you reach your goals, faster!\r\n\r\nGreat Flavors\r\nEfficacious Doses of CLA and Carnitine\r\nStim-Free',30.00,12,1,0.00,'2024-09-02 22:37:29','2024-09-02 22:37:29'),(135,'GLUTAMINE PURE (60 SERVINGS)','Glutamine is a crucial nutrient for muscle growth - comprising 60% of muscle amino acids. This vital supply diminishes due to intense training, dieting and stress - leading to muscle breakdown. Supplementing with L-Glutamine maintains optimal levels - so your muscle growth and recovery are optimized. GLUTAMINE PURE offers pure, unflavored L-Glutamine that mixes easily into any beverage. Include it during your post-workout routine to accelerate muscle repair and prime them for faster growth. Get your supply of GLUTAMINE PURE today.',20.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-09-02 22:51:46','2025-02-10 20:43:37'),(136,'MEN\'S MULTI (90 TABLETS)','We created Men\'s Multi Active Lifestyle to support the needs of highly active men. With over 50 ingredients, 24 vitamins and minerals, and a host of supporting compounds, this daily goes way beyond your typical grocery store multi.\r\nMen\'s Multi Active Lifestyle supplies all the basics plus digestive enzymes, amino acids, herbal extracts, a carotenoid complex, and phytonutrient-rich fruit concentrates. This is one powerful nutrient complex.\r\n \r\n\r\n50 active ingredients \r\n24 vitamins and essential minerals\r\n37.5mcg vitamin D3\r\n275mg+ B-complex vitamins\r\nAmino acids, enzymes, antioxidants, and phytonutrients\r\n \r\n\r\nZERO Calories\r\nZERO Sugars\r\nZERO Non-Functional Filler Ingredients',30.00,11,1,0.00,'2024-09-02 22:59:56','2025-05-26 20:44:00'),(137,'WOMEN\'S MULTI (60 TABLETS)','Our Women\'s Multi Active Lifestyle supports the needs of highly active women. With over 40 ingredients, antioxidants A, C, and E, high-potency iron, plus a host of supporting compounds, this daily goes way beyond your typical grocery store multi.\r\nWomen\'s Multi Active Lifestyle supplies all the basics plus herbal extracts, a carotenoid complex, and phytonutrient-rich fruit and vegetable concentrates. This is one powerful nutrient complex.^\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n40+ active ingredients\r\n25 vitamins and minerals\r\nIron, folate, calcium, and cranberry\r\nAntioxidant vitamins A, C, and E\r\n200% daily value vitamin D3†\r\nSuperfoods, herb extracts, isoflavones, and phytonutrients\r\n \r\n\r\nZERO Calories\r\nZERO Sugars\r\nZERO Banned Substances',25.00,11,0,0.00,'2024-09-02 23:09:54','2025-02-10 20:43:45'),(138,'COLLAGEN PEPTIDES (20 SERVINGS)','Our latest Collagen Peptides formula combines hydrolyzed collagen sources with hyaluronic acid and vitamin C to help support healthy skin, hair, nails, and joints.\r\nClean Formulation\r\nOur Collagen Peptides are free of dairy, gluten, and added sugars, which makes them suitable for a wide variety of eating plans. \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n10g collagen\r\n80mg Hyaluronic Acid\r\n100% Daily Value for Vitamin C\r\nSweetened with stevia (flavored varieties only)\r\nInstantized for easy mixing \r\n \r\n\r\nAvailable in easy-to-drink flavored and add-to-anything unflavored varieties, Collagen Peptides mix easily into your favorite hot or cold liquids.',30.00,15,1,0.00,'2024-09-02 23:33:44','2025-03-26 16:27:24'),(139,'Blade Sport, Blade Whey Plus (56 SERVINGS)','BLADE WHEY PLUS is made of the best sources ultra filtered whey protein concentrate and Casein to provide a multi-stage system that is designed to effectively nourish your muscles and maintain anabolism.\r\nWhey protein & Casein\r\n30g Protein & 4g BCAA per Serving\r\n4g Creatine per Serving\r\nGreat Mixability\r\nDelicious Taste\r\nBLADE WHEY PLUS is made of the best sources ultra filtered whey protein concentrate and Casein to provide a multi-stage system that is designed to effectively nourish your muscles and maintain anabolism. Each serving of BLADE WHEY PLUS contains 30 grams of protein and 4 grams of BCAA and 4g of Creatine, which are necessary for everybody who want to support quality muscle mass growth.\r\n\r\nBLADE WHEY PLUS complete protein formula has been designed for competitive bodybuilders, athletes and those carrying heavy physical work looking to build muscle in the shortest time possible. If you want to experience what the highest-quality protein powder has to offer, BLADE WHEY PLUS is the best choice.\r\n\r\nDIRECTIONS\r\nMix 1 scoop into 350ml of water. Can be taken anytime, before or after gym, day or night.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nProtein matrix (whey protein concentrate, milk protein concentrate, micellar casein concentrate), glutamine complex (glutamine peptide), L-glutamine, creatine monohydrate, cocoa powder, thickener (cellulose gum), flavor, emulsifier (soy lecithin), sweeteners: acesulfame K, sucralose, salt.',60.00,1,0,0.00,'2024-09-03 20:54:33','2025-04-10 18:41:49'),(140,'Pro-Antium Multifaceted Protein (52 servings)','Pro antrum is a multifaceted protein blend intended for complete recovery. This multifunctional blend contains a precise combination of fast, medium, and slow-digesting proteins for optimal recovery providing you with a continuous stream of protein long after your workout is complete. Each serving also contains 13.5g of essential amino acids as well as 3.5g of branched-chain amino acids. Pro antium doesn’t just stop at the protein blend. We have also added 5g of creatine and 2.5g of betaine which has been scientifically suggested to support strength, power, and athletic performance. Betaine increases the efficiency rate at which the body absorbs protein, creatine, and amino acids into muscle cells by supporting the body’s ability to break them down.\r\n\r\nBenefits\r\nProvides increased strength\r\nRebuild and recover muscles fast\r\nEnhances athletic performance\r\n5 grams of Creatine and 2.5 grams of Betaine together provides an environment for complete muscle growth and recovery\r\nProvides much-needed support for muscle recovery and excellent workout performance\r\nIngredients\r\nProtein Complex (Whey Protein Concentrate, Milk Protein Isolate, Calcium Caseinate, Whey Protein Isolate, Micellar Casein, Egg White Albumin), Creatine Monohydrate, Cocoa Powder, Betaine Anhydrous, Cookie Crumbs (Enriched Flour (Wheat Four, Niacin, Reduced Iron, Thiamine Mononitrate, Riboflavin, Folic Acid), Sugar, Cocoa processed with Alkali, Soybean and/or Palm Oils, High Fructose Corn Syrup, Chocolate Liquor, Salt, Com Flour, Dextrose, Sodium Bicarbonate, Soy Lecithin), Natural and Artificial Flavors,Maltodextrin, Gum Blend (Cellulose, Xanthan, Carrageenan), Caramel Powder (color), Sucralose, Flour Salt, Acesulfame Potassium, Creamer (Sunflower Oil, Maltodextrin, Sodium Caseinate, Mono and Diglycerides, Natural Tocopherols, Tricalcium Phosphate), Enzyme Blend (Protease, Amylase & Lactase), Soy Lecithin.',60.00,1,1,0.00,'2024-09-03 21:02:59','2024-09-03 21:02:59'),(141,'BLADE SPORT WHEY (75 SERVINGS)','76% Whey Protein Concentrate\r\n12% Whey Protein Isolate\r\n22g Protein & 4.5g BCAA per Serving\r\nGreat Mixability\r\nDelicious Taste\r\nBLADE WHEY is 100% pure whey protein with a high biological value, which uses only the most premium macronutrient sources. This innovative formula is made of the best sources ultrafiltered whey protein concentrate and whey protein isolate to provide a multi-stage system that is designed to effectively nourish your muscles and maintain anabolism. Each serving of BLADE WHEY contains 22 grams of protein and 4.5 grams of BCAA, which are necessary for everybody who want to support quality muscle mass growth.',60.00,1,0,0.00,'2024-09-03 21:24:04','2025-04-05 14:39:04'),(142,'T.A.G (40 SERVINGS)','T.A.G. or Trans Alanyl Glutamine, is the only true Muscle-Targeted Glutamine. Due to its unique di-peptide bond, T.A.G. creates a jacket to protect glutamine all the way through to the muscle. T.A.G. is an ideal solution for muscle repair, reducing muscle tissue degradation, and enhancing recovery.\r\n\r\nGlutamine has been a staple for athletes and fitness enthusiasts for benefits to muscle recovery and glutamine’s impact on the body’s immune system as a whole. While glutamine has many advantages to helping improve performance and health, it is often under-utilized in supplement programs due to poor absorption kinetics. However, T.A.G. has been scientifically engineered to deliver the full dose of glutamine necessary due to its unique bonding with alanine. Enhanced absorption means real results, and with enhanced recovery, you can go longer and stronger than ever before.',35.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-09-03 21:36:58','2025-05-19 15:13:51'),(155,'SUPPLEMENT STATION PROTEIN BAR (RED VELVET)','Each box contain 12 protein bar \r\nProtein bar only for 22$\r\nCalories 230\r\nlow fat, low sugar and carbs \r\n18g protein \r\nYou can take it as a Breakfast, post-workout and as a snack',2.00,19,1,0.00,'2024-09-07 23:47:42','2024-09-07 23:47:42'),(156,'SUPPLEMENT STATION PROTEIN BAR (COFFEE)','Each box contain 12 protein bar \r\nProtein bar only for 22$\r\nCalories 210\r\nlow fat, low sugar and carbs \r\n15g protein \r\nYou can take it as a Breakfast, post-workout and as a snack',2.00,19,1,0.00,'2024-09-07 23:53:38','2024-09-07 23:53:38'),(157,'SUPPLEMENT STATION PROTEIN BAR (CHOCOLETE BORWNIES)','Each box contain 12 protein bar \r\nProtein bar only for 22$\r\nCalories 240\r\nlow fat, low sugar and carbs \r\n18g protein \r\nYou can take it as a Breakfast, post-workout and as a snack',2.00,19,1,0.00,'2024-09-07 23:58:38','2024-09-07 23:58:38'),(158,'SUPPLEMENT STATION PROTEIN BAR (CARAMELIZED BISCUITS)','Each box contain 12 protein bar \r\nProtein bar only for 22$\r\nCalories 230\r\nlow fat, low sugar and carbs \r\n18g protein \r\nYou can take it as a Breakfast, post-workout and as a snack',2.00,19,1,0.00,'2024-09-08 00:06:02','2024-09-08 00:06:02'),(159,'SUPPLEMENT STATION PROTEIN BAR (PEANUT BUTTER)','Each box contain 12 protein bar \r\nProtein bar only for 22$\r\nCalories 250\r\nlow fat, low sugar and carbs \r\n20g protein \r\nYou can take it as a Breakfast, post-workout and as a snack',2.00,19,1,0.00,'2024-09-08 00:13:09','2024-09-08 00:13:09'),(160,'GYM GLOVES','Training Gloves are made with breathable, lightweight materials for enhanced flexibility. They have a smart hook-and-loop wrist closure to let you find the perfect fit. Designed with light padding on the palm that adds a layer of protection between you and your workout.',10.00,17,1,0.00,'2024-09-10 23:07:16','2024-09-11 18:18:58'),(161,'NITRO TECH 100% WHEY GOLD (69 servings)','24g protein \r\n5.3g bcaa\r\n4g glutamine & precursor \r\nFor more than two decades, the groundbreaking Nitro-Tech formula has taken all challengers – and is still recognized as one of the most powerful proteins ever developed.\r\nFeaturing high-quality whey protein, this ultra-pure, rapidly  absorbed and quickly digested protein is scientifically engineered to support fast recovery, help you build more lean muscle mass and give you better results from your training sessions.',65.00,1,0,0.00,'2024-09-10 23:33:29','2025-02-10 20:44:58'),(162,'RULE 1 CITRULLINE (60 SERVINGS)','3g citrulline \r\nCitrulline contributes to nitric oxide synthesis which supports muscle pumps and training performance making this amino acid a popular foundational staple for any serious lifter .\r\nPump and Endurance Support\r\nIn addition to levels synthesized by the body, citrulline can be supplemented to help support muscle pumps and endurance. Made with pure l-citrulline, our foundation series powder contains no flavors, sweeteners, or fillers. Each scoop mixes readily into all your favorite beverages and workout supplements for convenient supplement enhancement.',25.00,6,0,0.00,'2024-09-10 23:44:46','2025-02-10 20:45:14'),(163,'ZINC 50MG (100 TABLETS)','Zinc is essential to the normal function of many organs and systems within the body including the skeletal, immune, neurological, and endocrine systems. Zinc is a necessary mineral co-factor for hundreds of enzymatic reactions related to protein and carbohydrate metabolism, RNA/DNA synthesis, and intercellular signaling. It is also known to play a critical role in the body’s free radical neutralizing activities and is especially helpful for maintenance of healthy aging.',15.00,11,0,0.00,'2024-09-11 00:16:26','2025-02-10 20:45:26'),(164,'UNIVERSAL CARBO PLUS (55 SERVINGS)','Engineered for endurance and strength athletes alike, Carbo Plus™ fuels your body with pure complex carbohydrates without any added simple sugars, sweeteners, preservatives, fillers, or artificial flavors. Carbo Plus can function as an important source of energy for your working muscles during strenuous exercise. By training with Carbo Plus™, you can maximize the replenishment of glycogen in your muscle and liver. This translates into enhanced performance, faster muscle recovery, and higher endurance levels.\r\nSlowly blend 1 scoop of Carbo Plus into 8-10oz of your beverage of choice. For best results, use at least twice daily and consume 1 serving within 2 hours of exercise.',25.00,13,1,0.00,'2024-09-11 01:02:55','2024-09-11 01:02:55'),(165,'THUNDER GAIN (16 SERVINGS)','For serious athletes and bodybuilders, there’s a right way and a wrong way to gain weight. Thunder Gain weight gainer product will help you put on pounds in a healthy, efficient, and delicious way. Thunder.\r\nThunder Gain contains pure whey protein concentrate and packs a punch with 1,250 calories per 334-gram serving. You’ll also get 50 full grams of protein and essential nutrients with each dose, including calcium, iron, and potassium.\r\n\r\nWe’ve designed this weight gainer for hardcore individuals looking to increase size and build strength faster. This high-calorie protein plus carbohydrate powder maximizes muscle mass while supplying energy to support muscle building. It also mixes well, is easy to digest, and has a delicious flavors taste.\r\n\r\nTrue challengers don’t accept anything less than the best. Thunder Gain is a great weight gainer available today for developing your physique to the fullest.',55.00,4,1,0.00,'2024-09-11 01:07:19','2025-04-02 17:45:43'),(167,'Gym Belts','Weight Lifting Belts are ergonomically designed to provide Firm & Comfortable Lumbar Support during any kind of Strength Training.\r\n\r\nReduce spinal flexion creating safer biomechanics when lifting and provides superior back and abdominal support and is hand washable with Air Dry.\r\nBelt is ergonomically designed to fit the natural shape of the body while stabilizing the core muscles\r\nThis durable and comfortable weight lifting belt is a must-have for any athlete serious about their fitness.\r\nProfessional design: NOT only is our contoured work out belt light, durable, & strong, there are no predetermined holes limiting your adjustability.\r\nPerfect for weight training - Whether you Do Cross fit, powerlifting, Olympic lifting or just a weekend warrior weight training newbie, you can rest assured\r\nCoactive quality promise - this belt was designed with the quality you are looking for',20.00,17,1,0.00,'2024-09-11 17:47:48','2024-09-11 18:20:25'),(168,'wrist wrap','Thanks to the thumb insert, these wrist straps are easy to put on and keep your wrist joint aligned during weight lifting exercises.\r\n\r\nWith their short strap and rip-tab closure, these wrist straps prevent abnormal tension and twisting of the joint during dumbbell, barbell, or kettlebell exercises',5.00,17,1,0.00,'2024-09-11 18:03:55','2024-09-11 18:21:35'),(169,'Lifting straps','This lifting straps provide excellent grip, relieving pressure on your hands and forearms and thus helping you improve the execution of your lifting exercises.\r\n\r\nThese straps are easy to store and essential to your strength training or body building workouts',5.00,17,1,0.00,'2024-09-11 18:10:47','2024-09-11 18:15:11'),(170,'EAA ZERO 350 g','FLAVOURED DIETARY SUPPLEMENT DRINK POWDER WITH ESSENTIAL AMINO ACIDS, L-GLUTAMINE AND SWEETENERS.\r\n7160mg essential amino acid content\r\nIt is the essential amino acid ratio recommended by the WHO\r\nClose to 1:1 ratio of glutamine and BCAA\r\nSugar-free\r\nGluten-free\r\nIt refers to ready shakes mixed with water.\r\nThe ratio of the different essential amino acids in the product follows the recommendation of the World Health Organization (WHO). (Protein and Amino Acid Requirements in Human Nutrition – Report from the Joint FAO/WHO/UNU Expert Consultation.)\r\n\r\nEssential amino acids, as the name implies, are indispensable for the human body since it either cannot produce them at all or it can produce them only in quantities that are insufficient. That is why it is particularly important to ensure their intake from external sources, preferably in optimal quantities and in the right proportions.\r\n\r\nAs with all BioTechUSA products, EAA Zero was also developed to have the best composition. Therefore, EAA Zero contains all the essential amino acids in optimal proportion as set out by the World Health Organization.\r\n\r\nDuring the renewal of EAA Zero we didn’t only seek to get the proportions right, but we also aimed at creating a complex product. As a result, the product now contains all the essential amino acids and by adding glutamine we further increased the quantity of amino acids required for muscle building.\r\n\r\nEAA Zero provides a special amino acid combination that you can drink without guilt even if you are on a diet, because the product is sugar-free. Drink it in refreshing lemon and blue grape flavours before or even during an exhaustive workout session.',30.00,8,1,0.00,'2024-09-14 20:26:17','2024-09-14 20:26:17'),(171,'100% CREATINE Monohydrate (88 SERVINGS)','100% Creatine Monohydrate is made from pure powdered creatine monohydrate. Due to the tasteless powder form, it can be easily mixed with other food supplements, e.g. weight gainers or protein-based beverage powders.\r\nPure & Powdered Performance\r\n\r\nCreatine increases your performance in a successive burst of short-term, high-intensity exercises. The beneficial effect is obtained with a daily intake of 3 g of creatine. 100% Creatine Monohydrate is prepared with pure, pharmaceutical-grade creatine in powdered form. It’s flavorless so it’s easy to mix with other supplements like weight gainers and protein shakes. Like all BioTech USA products, 100% Creatine Monohydrate is a safe, carefully selected nutrient.',25.00,3,0,0.00,'2024-09-14 20:37:06','2025-05-26 20:40:28'),(172,'ASHWAGANDHA (60 capsules)','Ashwagandha is a plant from Southeast Asia that is used as an ancient adaptogen. Although it is not a member of the ginseng family but that of the potato family, it is often referred to as Indian ginseng because it is used in the Ayurvedic medicine in the same way as ginseng in the Chinese medicine. Often we can also come across the name dream berry. The roots and leaves of the plant are most often used in dried and ground form in everyday life, even in shakes, mixed with different pasty foods.',16.00,10,1,0.00,'2024-09-14 20:47:43','2024-09-14 20:47:43'),(173,'MILK THISTLE (60 CAPSULES)','Milk Thistle’s active substance has been used as an herbal remedy for a long time. Dietary supplements with milk thistle are popular among elderly, athletes and everybody leading a healthy lifestyle.\r\nmilk thistle extract\r\nMilk Thistle (Sylibum marianum) related to the group of thistles and to the daisy and ragweed family. It is native to the Mediterranean countries, to North-Africa and to Near East. It has many common names such as Mary thistle or holy thistle. Its growth is the achenium and its active substance silymarin is extracted from this. Milk Thistle’s active substance has been used as an herbal remedy for a long time. Dietary supplements with milk thistle are popular among elderly, athletes and everybody leading a healthy lifestyle.\r\n\r\nBenefits\r\nNatural plant extract\r\n210 mg silymarin content per capsule\r\nEconomic packaging size for two months\r\nDirections of use\r\nTake 1 capsule a day with a glass of water.',15.00,10,0,0.00,'2024-09-14 20:52:48','2025-05-22 17:01:14'),(174,'ISO WHEY ZERO 500G','Premium whey protein isolate drink powder, with reduced lactose content, sugar1 and gluten-free2, with added BCAA and glutamine amino acids, sugars, and sweetener.',35.00,2,0,0.00,'2024-09-14 21:01:57','2025-03-08 15:45:06'),(175,'ISO WHEY ZERO 908G','Premium whey protein isolate drink powder, with reduced lactose content, sugar1 and gluten-free2, with added BCAA and glutamine amino acids, sugars, and sweetener. \r\nNative Whey Isolate basic ingredient\r\nOutstanding protein content\r\nWith added amino acids: L-glutamine and BCAA\r\nFast and easy absorption\r\nFree of sugar*, lactose* and gluten\r\nNo preservatives\r\nAspartame-free\r\nIn case of powder supplements, the statement applies to products dissolved in water and ready to consume.\r\n\r\nOur Native Whey Isolate is produced directly from fresh milk by pasteurisation followed by micro and ultra filtration at low temperatures, and then pulverisation in a special drying chamber. Due to this unique procedure, the protein structure is preserved in its fullest form and it also remains rich in immunoglobulin (antibody) and lactoferrin (part of your immune system). Also, the raw material is free from chemicals and any other contaminants.\r\nZERO COMPROMISE\r\n\r\nDue to its outstanding protein content, it’s a perfect choice for active athletes who make all efforts for a lean body, but it is also a great alternative for those on a diet.\r\n1 Per serving (25 g):\r\n\r\n93 kcal\r\n21 g protein\r\nof which 4.5 g BCAA',50.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-09-14 21:11:24','2025-03-08 15:45:33'),(176,'CARBOX (20 SERVINGS)','Carbox is a drink powder containing a carbohydrate complex. It combines five forms of slow, moderate and fast absorbing carbohydrates. It contains maltodextrin, dextrose, saccharose, fructose and corn starch. These sugars have different glycemic indexes, that is, they affect blood sugar levels to different extents. Due to their varied absorption rates, some of them supply your body with carbs quickly, whereas the others for prolonged periods.\r\nBenefits\r\n increases energy after training\r\n contains 5 types of carbohydrates\r\n gluten-free\r\n replenishes glycogen stores\r\nCarbox also makes a great companion during post-workout recovery. The carbs it contains contribute to the recovery of normal muscle function (contraction) after high-intensity and/or prolonged physical exercise which leads to muscle exhaustion and the depletion of the glycogen stores of core muscles\r\n\r\nDirections of use\r\nMix 1 serving (50 g = 3 heaped tablespoons) with 300 ml water, or, in the case of unflavoured Carbox, with any liquid of your choice. Consume 1 serving before and during workout or competition.',16.00,13,1,0.00,'2024-09-14 21:16:35','2024-09-14 21:16:35'),(177,'PROTEIN POWER (33 SERVINGS)','BioTechUSA Protein Power is prepared with high quality soy and milk proteins, and delivers a whole range of BCAAs, L-Glutamine and other essential and non-essential amino acids.\r\n80% Protein content\r\nSugar-free\r\nFat-free\r\nGluten-free\r\nLactose-free\r\n1,500 mg Creatine per serving\r\nExcellent price-to-value ratio\r\nBioTech USA Protein Power is a great protein powder for dedicated athletes looking for high protein content. Like all BioTech USA products, Protein Power consists of safe and carefully selected nutrients. Prepared with high quality milk and soy proteins, Protein Power delivers a whole range of BCAAs, L-Glutamine and other essential and non-essential amino acids. It ensures a long lasting anabolic and anti-catabolic environment in your body witch is optimal for extreme muscle building. Its protein content contributes to the growth and maintenance of the muscle mass. The product also contains added creatine.\r\n\r\nProtein Power is a quite popular product of Biotech USA since it is the best value for your money on the protein market today.\r\n\r\nDIRECTIONS\r\nMix 1 serving (30 g) with 300 ml water and drink 1-2 times a day. Use a shaker to prepare your drink. Drink one serving within 45 minutes after workout, and another one between two meals. On rest days, drink 1 serving in the morning and 1 serving in the evening.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS (Chocolate):\r\nProtein Blend 71% [soy protein isolate, whey protein concentrate, calcium caseinate (contains milk)], fat-reduced cocoa powder, flavour enhancer (glycine and its sodium salt), micronized creatine monohydrate 5%, flavourings, anti-caking agent (magnesium salts of fatty acids, silicon dioxide), salt, emulsifier: lecithins (soy), sweeteners (sucralose, acesulfame K), thickener (cellulose gum).',33.00,1,0,0.00,'2024-09-14 21:23:35','2025-05-06 17:01:52'),(178,'VEGAN PROTEIN','Bulking up with the power of plant-based protein sources\r\nPackaging made with reduced amount of plastic.\r\nVegan protein complex (rice and peas)\r\nWith added amino acids: L-glutamine and L-arginine\r\nSugar- and lactose-free*\r\nGluten-free\r\nNo preservatives\r\nNo artificial colour\r\nNon-GMO\r\nAspartame-free\r\nWith 3 types of superfoods\r\n88 mg caffeine per serving\r\nIt refers to ready shakes mixed with water.',30.00,20,0,0.00,'2024-09-14 21:36:18','2025-02-26 17:04:50'),(179,'BIOTECH BEEF PROTEIN (60 SERVINGS)','BioTechUSA Hydrolyzed Beef Protein is one of the best protein sources from bovine meat without lactose, sugar or gluten!\r\n26 g Beef Protein Blend – Protein complex that contains only beef protein hydrolysate with added L-glutamine and L-arginine amino acids\r\n4.5 g BCAA, 10 g essential amino acid, 8 g conditionally essential amino acid\r\nLow fat and carbohydrate content\r\nWith added vitamin complex, including metabolism normalising vitamins B3, B6 and B12\r\nWithout added creatine\r\nIdeal for Paleo diet\r\nSugar-free, Gluten-free, Lactose-free\r\nHydrolyzed protein provided by bovine meat, one of the best protein sources that can be found, without Lactose, Sugar Or Gluten!\r\n\r\nHydroBeef™ is a peptide formula gained from European beef through multistep hydrolysis, containing a special blend of amino acids and pre-digested peptides of various molecular sizes.\r\n\r\nHydroBeef™ is a protein source which is easier to digest than low-fat beef (e. g. steak), absorbs within 60 minutes and has a high protein and nitrogen value (100). The brand new lactose and soy-free BioTechUSA Beef Protein is based on this cholesterol-free protein source of over 97% purity.\r\n\r\nIts protein content contributes to muscle mass growth and maintenance. The natural vitamin and mineral content improves the absorption of nutrients, of which vitamin B6 contributes to normal protein and glycogen metabolism as well as reducing tiredness and fatigue. It is an excellent supplement to a Paleo diet.\r\n\r\nDuring the elaboration process of Beef Protein, no chemicals are ever used. In the production process the microfiltration and hydrolysis technique is used, to produce a truly pure product with a high peptide arrangement. This way, all the essential nutrients will be kept intact, both peptides, amino acids, nucleotide fractions, and vitamins & minerals.\r\n\r\nIn addition, it offers an optimum digestion, solubility and absorption due to the carefully monitorised process of elaboration.\r\n\r\nLike all BioTech USA products, Beef Protein consists of safe and carefully selected ingredients.\r\n\r\nWe recommend Beef Protein:\r\n\r\nAs an excellent protein source for anyone, it contributes to the maintenance of healthy bones and muscle mass, as well as to muscle mass growth.\r\nAs a protein supplement to a dairy-free diet\r\nIf you keep a Paleo diet\r\nIf you are Lactose intolerant\r\nIf you are Celiac (suffer from gluten-intolerance)\r\nDirections\r\nMix 1 serving (30 g) of powder with 250 ml water or skimmed milk. Take 2 servings a day. Take the first serving within 45 minutes after workout and the other serving between meals. On non-workout days take 1 serving in the morning.',80.00,14,0,0.00,'2024-09-14 22:08:03','2025-05-30 15:22:01'),(180,'ISO WHEY ZERO 2270G (90 SERVINGS)','Premium whey protein isolate drink powder, with reduced lactose content, sugar1 and gluten-free2, with added BCAA and glutamine amino acids, sugars, and sweetener. \r\nBiotech USA Iso Whey Zero is a premium quality sugar-free, lactose-free and gluten-free whey protein isolate with native whey isolate basic ingredient, added BCAAs and amino acids. Because of its high protein content it is an excellent choice for active sportspeople or for those who work hard for a tight and toned body, but it can help people to compile their diet.\r\n\r\nBenefits\r\n high purity premium whey isolate\r\n produced from fresh milk after pasteurisation and micro and ultra-filtering\r\n extremely fast and easy absorbability\r\n accelerates the growth of lean muscles\r\n promotes protection and maintenance of muscle mass\r\n improves recovery after hard workouts\r\n up to 84% of protein per serving\r\n low carbohydrate and fat content\r\nadded sugar, gluten and lactose FREE\r\n excellent solubility and delicious taste\r\nPERFORMANCE STARTS WITH THE BASIC INGREDIENTS!\r\nOur Native Whey Protein Isolate is produced directly from fresh milk after pasteurisation and micro and ultra-filtering at low temperature, which is afterwards pulverised in a special drying chamber. Thanks to this unique procedure the protein structure is preserved in its fullest form, and it remains rich in immunoglobulin (antibodies) and lactoferrin (which is part of the immune system).\r\n\r\nWHY DO YOU NEED TO TAKE PROTEINS?\r\nProtein is an essential building block in our bodies. It is a source of nutrition consisting of amino acids produced by the body or taken in from external sources. It helps to retain your muscles during workout, dieting or everyday life. Your need for protein increases if you regularly do sports, or if you want to grow muscle mass or when you start ageing.\r\n\r\nWHY SHOULD YOU TAKE PROTEIN SUPPLEMENTS?\r\nThe consumption of protein shakes is a fast, practical and highly effective way to ensure the right protein intake. You only need the protein powder, a shaker and some water for it.Protein powder can be made from milk, but it can be derived from animals or plants, as well a combination of these. Their absorption can be fast (30 - 40 min), medium (1 - 2 hours) or slow (longer than 2 hours).\r\n\r\nWe recommend Iso Whey Zero if you:\r\nare looking for an excellent source of protein which contributes to maintaining muscle mass and healthy bones as well as to muscle mass growth\r\nwant to use high-quality protein products for your protein needs but need to avoid lactose due to your intolerance\r\nseek a fast absorbing post-workout protein powder for recovery\r\nseek low-calorie sweets during a diet\r\nare sensitive to gluten\r\nlike nice and varied flavours',100.00,2,1,0.00,'2024-09-14 22:15:50','2024-09-14 22:15:50'),(181,'100% PURE WHEY 2270G (81 SERVINGS)','Excellent whey protein enriched with bromelain enzyme, extra amino acids, free of gluten, aspartame, preservatives and added sugar. 100% Pure Whey is suitable for athletes, as well as ordinary people, who want to accelerate muscle growth, provide the muscles with all the necessary amino acids, maximize their sports performance, ensure sufficient daily intake of high quality protein and support recovery after hard workouts.\r\nBenefits\r\n promotes lean muscle growth\r\n maximizes sports performance\r\n accelerates and improves recovery\r\n high biological value of proteins\r\n up to 75% of protein per serving\r\n low carbohydrate and fat content\r\n added extra amino acids and bromelain enzyme\r\n high BCAAs content (up to 6 g per serving)\r\n easy digestibility and rapid absorption\r\n excellent solubility and delicious taste\r\n free of gluten, aspartame, preservatives and added sugar\r\nWHY 100% PURE WHEY?\r\nIt is a high-quality protein shake with a high BV (biological value) and 75% protein content that is 100% derived from whey protein. The wide-ranging flavours of 100% Pure Whey is a combination of whey protein concentrate, whey protein isolate and added amino acids (L-glutamine, L-arginine and BCAAs). The non-flavoured version contains only whey protein concentrate, without any added sweeteners, colouring or flavouring.\r\n\r\nWe recommend 100% Pure Whey if you:\r\n\r\nwant an excellent protein source, because the protein content of the product contributes to the growth and maintenance of muscle mass as well as to healthy and normal bones\r\nare looking for quick solution to regenerate after workout\r\nare celiac\r\nprefer delicious, varied and creamy flavours\r\nWHY DO YOU NEED TO TAKE PROTEINS?\r\nProtein is an essential building block in our bodies. It is a source of nutrition consisting of amino acids produced by the body or taken in from external sources. It helps to retain your muscles during workout, dieting or everyday life. Your need for protein increases if you regularly do sports, or if you want to grow muscle mass or when you start ageing.\r\n\r\nWHY SHOULD YOU TAKE PROTEIN SUPPLEMENTS?\r\nThe consumption of protein shakes is a fast, practical and highly effective way to ensure the right protein intake. You only need the protein powder, a shaker and some water or milk for it. Protein powder is easy to digest and contrary to large amounts of meat consumption, it doesn’t cause acidity. Protein powder can be made from milk, but it can be derived from animals or plants, as well a combination of these. Their absorption can be fast (30 - 40 min), medium (1 - 2 hours) or slow (longer than 2 hours).\r\n\r\nDirections of use\r\nMix 1 serving (28 g = 1 scoop = 2 tablespoons) of powder with 250 ml water or skimmed milk. Take 2 servings daily. Take the first serving within 45 minutes after workout and the other serving between meals. Use a shaker!',80.00,1,1,0.00,'2024-09-14 22:22:57','2025-05-06 17:02:00'),(182,'EAA+ HYDRATION (30 SERVINGS)','Elevate your performance, maximize recovery and refuel with EAA+ Hydration, the ultimate fusion of essential amino acids and advanced hydration. Unleash your potential with 8g of all 9 EAAs and 6g of BCAAs in a proven 2:1:1 ratio, supercharging muscle recovery, growth, and electrolyte balance. Power through your toughest workouts, redefine limits, and become unstoppable. This is more than EAAs – it’s total recovery, hydration and relentless fuel for your journey to excellence. Elevate with EAA+ Hydration now.',25.00,8,1,0.00,'2024-09-14 22:41:56','2025-04-22 15:16:40')