e.',25.00,6,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 19:13:56','2025-05-19 15:14:06'),(197,'Nutritech Premium Mass Builder','NutriTech Premium Mass Builder is a high-calorie, nutrient-rich supplement powder designed to help individuals gain weight and build muscle mass. It contains a blend of proteins, carbohydrates, vitamins, and minerals to support muscle growth and recovery.',55.00,4,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 19:22:30','2025-05-19 15:15:08'),(198,'Nutritech Premium Whey Protein','Nutritech Premium Whey Protein 2kg is a special formulation of ingredients to support lean muscle growth, muscle recovery, and strength gains post workout. The fast-absorbing, high protein blend is ideal for consumption after working out, or just as a general supplement throughout the day.',55.00,1,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 19:25:44','2025-05-19 15:14:50'),(199,'NUTRITECH VASO PRE-WORKOUT','VASO N03 has been formulated as a nitric oxide pre-workout concentrate. Massive pump and vascularity without the crash! ZERO Caffeine or Stimulants. The combination of ingredients in VASO N03 creates a synergistic powerhouse that supercharges exercise performance, boosts endurance, increases power output, reduces fatigue, and supports recovery, providing you with a comprehensive solution for maximizing your workout potential.',25.00,9,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 19:32:27','2025-02-13 19:32:27'),(200,'Flavoured Creatine Monohydrate 250g','Creatine Monohydrate is suitable for anyone partaking in prolonged or high-intensity exercise, looking to improve physical performance. Applied Nutrition’s Creatine provides the purest, most readily absorbed Creatine Monohydrate available. Studies report that the increase of creatine levels will help delay the onset of fatigue, increase energy metabolism in the muscle cells and enhance the body\'s overall training capability.',20.00,3,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 19:38:10','2025-03-26 16:25:30'),(201,'LARRY WHEELS ISOLATE PROTEIN 25 SERVINGS','Introducing the Personal Records Supplements - Larry Wheels Series Isolate Protein, the ultimate protein supplement designed with the renowned fitness sensation, Larry Wheels.\r\n\r\nThis cutting-edge product has been meticulously crafted to help you reach new heights in your fitness journey and smash personal records like never before. Harnessing the combined expertise of Personal Records Supplements and Larry Wheels, this premium isolate protein is a true game-changer.\r\n\r\nPacked with high-quality, fast-absorbing whey protein isolate, it delivers a potent dose of essential amino acids to fuel your muscles and support optimal recovery. Each serving ensures you get the purest form of protein, free from unnecessary fillers, so you can maximize every workout and achieve peak performance.\r\n\r\nThe Personal Records Supplements - Larry Wheels Series Isolate Protein is not just about raw power – it also caters to your taste buds. Crafted with an array of delicious flavors, it transforms your post-workout ritual into a delectable treat, making sure you never miss a scoop.\r\n\r\nSay goodbye to bland and boring protein shakes and embrace the delightful experience this supplement provides. What sets this isolate protein apart is its commitment to transparency and quality. Rigorously tested for purity and potency, it meets the highest industry standards, ensuring you get only the best in every scoop.\r\n\r\nWith Personal Records Supplements and Larry Wheels\' joint dedication to excellence, you can have full confidence that this supplement is reliable and effective. Whether you\'re a seasoned athlete, a fitness enthusiast, or just starting your fitness journey, the Personal Records Supplements - Larry Wheels Series Isolate Protein is your ultimate partner in unlocking your true potential.\r\n\r\nEmbrace the power of this protein supplement and let it propel you towards achieving new personal records and surpassing your fitness goals. Fuel your body, ignite your performance, and set the bar higher with the Personal Records Supplements - Larry Wheels Series Isolate Protein – the embodiment of strength, quality, and unparalleled results. Experience the difference and step into a new realm of fitness supremacy.\r\n\r\nDirections Of Use\r\nMix 1 scoop with 6-8 ounces of cold water and drink immediately after workout or strenuous activity was also be taken anytime to promote recovery and help build strong muscles',35.00,2,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 19:47:23','2025-02-13 19:47:23'),(202,'TruFuel Tribulus Tribulus 750mg – 90 Capsules','Premium Tribulus Formula\r\n\r\nSupporting and Stimulating Testosterone.\r\n\r\nTruFuel Tribulus potentially boost testosterone levels naturally. Believed to support athletic performance and vitality, Tribulus supplements have gained popularity among individuals seeking to enhance their workout routines and overall vitality.',25.00,7,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 19:57:26','2025-02-13 19:57:26'),(203,'Trufuel Tongkat Ali','TruFuel Tongkat Ali, also known as Eurycome longifolia, is a southeast Asian botanical renowned for its potential benefits in enhancing libido, testosterone levels, and athletic performance, with traditional use extending to energy and vitality enhancement.',25.00,7,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:02:01','2025-02-13 20:02:01'),(204,'Caffeine + Taurine 60 capsules','80 mg of caffeine\r\n600 mg of taurine\r\nCaffeine + Taurin is an excellent alternative to poorly dosed and high carbohydrate energy drinks.\r\n100% gluten free product!\r\nCaffeine + Taurin, like all other BioTech USA products, contains safe, carefully selected nutrients.',13.00,9,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:10:03','2025-02-13 20:10:03'),(205,'LIVER AID','Choline and antioxidants: The choline content of Liver Aid contributes to the maintenance of normal liver function. The formula is enriched with antioxidants; selenium, Vitamins C and E contribute to the protection of the cells against oxidative stress. Due to the selenium, D and C vitamin content the formula also contributes to the normal function of the immune system.\r\n\r\nHerbal complex: The ingredients also include 8 well-known plants and their extracts. Let’s see them one by one: curcuma, milk thistle, greater burdock, chamomile, artichoke, chlorella algae, ayurvedic amla fruit and Andrographis.\r\n\r\nValuable amino acids: Proteins are among others one of the major components of living cells; amino acids are building blocks of proteins. Our body is unable to produce certain amino acids, for example L-methionine. These are called essential amino acids. L-cysteine is a conditional amino acid, which can be produced by the human body. Furthermore cysteine is also the building block of glutathione (GSH).\r\n\r\nFor men and women.\r\nFor a normal liver function due to the product’s choline content.\r\nEven if you have a varied diet.\r\nFor those who are looking for a dietary supplement with a complex content.\r\nHOW TO USE\r\nTake 2×1 tablet daily with a glass of water after main meals. Do not exceed the recommended dosage.',23.00,10,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:13:37','2025-05-22 17:01:39'),(206,'BioTech Citrulline Malate (300g)','pump product\r\nGluten free\r\nWithout aspartame\r\nPowder form for multiple uses\r\nfor a better supply of the muscles with oxygen and nutrients\r\nBioTechUSA Citrulline Malate contains the amino acid L-Citrulline in its pure form and with a \"neutral\" taste, no artificial additives, sugar and carbohydrates. L-citrulline is particularly popular before strength and endurance training. Most athletes already notice a noticeable effect during the first training session. There\'s a reason citrulline malate is one of the most popular and important ingredients in various pre-workout products. While citrulline malate is often combined with the amino acid L-arginine in bodybuilding and strength training, endurance athletes often benefit from a combination of citrulline malate and beta-alanine.',27.00,6,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:16:58','2025-05-14 16:36:58'),(208,'Biotech Citrulline Malate 90 capsules','do endurance sports, to be taken prior to or during workout\r\nare a bodybuilder\r\ndo functional trainings\r\nare sensitive to additives\r\nLike all BioTech USA products, Citrulline Malate capsule consists of safe and carefully selected ingredients.\r\n\r\nL-citrulline is a non-essential (conditionally essential) amino acid micro nutrient that the body cannot produce in sufficient quantities typically under greater strain, therefore replenishment might become necessary. When it comes to fruit, citrulline is found in large quantities in watermelon, for example. The synergistic combination of L-citrulline amino acid and malic acid is L-citrulline malate. Malic acid (malate) is an organic acid, which can be found in nature (for example in apple). L-citrulline amino acid is what L-arginine and L-ornithine amino acids are made of.\r\n\r\nIt is a formula very popular among athletes.',25.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:22:09','2025-05-07 15:48:28'),(209,'Zinc Duo 60 tablets','25 mg of zinc in a daily dose\r\nActive, easy-to-use formula\r\nContains 2 types of organic* zinc\r\nzinc bisglycinate (amino acid chelate)\r\nzinc gluconate\r\nSufficient packaging for 60 days\r\nThe gluconate compound belongs to organic* bonds and the elemental zinc content is adequate. Chelation is a type of bonding of inorganic zinc with amino acid creating an organic*, bisglycinate complex, which can be easily used by the human body.',15.00,11,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:32:54','2025-05-07 20:17:31'),(210,'One - A - Day multivitamin 100 tablets','Do you prefer easy, but effective solutions? Then One-A-Day multivitamin tablets with 12 types of vitamins and 10 types of minerals are an excellent choice for you! Thanks to its complex composition, it is suitable for you if you live an active lifestyle and follow a balanced diet, but you want to give some extra help for your body.',23.00,11,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:35:08','2025-04-11 16:31:01'),(211,'VICTOR MARTINEZ BCAA 5G JUICE 2:1:1, 30 SERVINGS','Branched Chain Amino Acids (BCAAs) is easily one of the best supplements you can take for aiding your fitness goals. One of the biggest reasons to use BCAAs is to improve your physical performance. Scientific evidence shows that they may help build muscles, reduce workout fatigue and decrease muscle soreness after exercise. Studies show that 5-10 grams of BCAA prior to or during your workout helps reduce muscle fatigue, improves muscle recovery, and increases energy',25.00,8,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:39:13','2025-04-24 19:42:05'),(212,'ULTRA COLLAGEN 30 SERVINGS','Type I and III Collagen Peptides\r\nGrass Fed & Unflavored\r\nPaleo and Keto Friendly\r\nNon-GMO and Gluten Free\r\nFeed your inner beauty with Unflavored Ultra Collagen Powder from Nature’s Truth! Collagen is one of the most abundant proteins in the body, and is naturally found in the muscles, bones, skin, and tendons. Created from grass fed, pasture-raised bovine, our Unflavored Ultra Collagen Powder provides 6,700 mg of Collagen Peptides Type 1 and 3 (from bovine) per serving, delivering 20 grams of Collagen, when taken the recommended three times daily.\r\n\r\nReap all the amazing benefits of collagen in this convenient, unflavored powder formula! Simply stir into any hot or cold drink, a smoothie, or your favorite recipe. This easily absorbable powder dissolves quickly and is odorless and flavor-free!\r\n\r\nDIRECTIONS\r\nFor adults, mix approximately one (1) heaping tablespoon (6.7 g) of Collagen three times daily (20 g Collagen) with 200-250 ml of cold or hot liquid. Stir vigorously or use blender for best results. For optimum benefits, take on an empty stomach and wait 30 minutes before eating.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS\r\nCollagen Peptides Type I & III (from Bovine).\r\n\r\nNO gluten, wheat, yeast, milk, lactose, soy, artificial color, artificial flavor, artificial sweetener, preservatives.\r\n\r\nSupplement Facts\r\nServing Size: 1 Scoop (6.7 g)\r\nServings Per Container: About 30',25.00,15,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:41:28','2025-04-22 15:19:24'),(213,'Giant Sports Edge Creatine Monohydrate, 500g','Creatine Powder - Each serving of Gaint Sports Edge Series creatine contains 5000mg of pure creatine monohydrate to help support strength and endurance\r\nMicronized Creatine - Giant Edge Creatine uses pure, micronized creatine to allow maximum mixabilty\r\nPre Workout or Post Workout - Giant Edge creatine is unflavored and mixes easily with any beverage and can be consumed pre workout or post workout to help support muscular strength and recovery.\r\nEnergy and Endurance - Supplementing with Creatine can help produce more ATP and allow men and women to train harder as ATP helps serve as fuel for muscles during exercise.\r\nHigh Quality Supplement - All Giant Sports Edge Series products are manufactured in the USA in a GMP compliant facility. All products are also third party lab tested for purity.',25.00,3,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:45:13','2025-03-24 17:39:48'),(214,'Muscle & Joint Fix - Recovery and Joint Support 90 capsules','To perform at your best, you need to feel your best. BPI Sports Titan Series Muscle & Joint Fix helps to keep you at the top of your game. This robust joint support formula contains clinically studied ingredients shown to help alleviate joint pain and to help protect against further damage. Muscle & Joint Fix can also be used as a recovery product.*\r\n\r\nAll-Natural Joint Support:\r\nMuscle & Joint Fix contains all-natural herbs that have been used in traditional medicine all over the world for years. White Peony and Turmeric Extract (containing curcumin) contain strong anti-inflammatory properties that can help repair joint damage and relieve pain.*\r\nRecover and Repair:\r\nWhite Peony and Turmeric contain antioxidants that can protect cells from free radicals and oxidative stress. By protecting our bodies and by increasing the production of collagen, Muscle and Joint Fix may help you recover faster from tough workouts and training sessions.*\r\nIncrease Collagen Production:\r\nHydrolyzed Beef Collagen is derived from cows and has been clinically shown to increase the production of type I and type III collagen. Collagen is important for the support of bones, tendons, and ligaments. An increase in collagen may relieve symptoms of arthritis and may prevent bone loss in older adults.*',30.00,10,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:48:35','2025-02-13 20:48:35'),(215,'B4 - Weight Loss And Energy 30 capsules','A truly unique option for Thermogenic \"Fat-Burners.\"\r\nB4™ is a dual sports performance supplement that not only works as a pre-workout but as a weight-loss supplement as well. Double duty sports performance supplement that keeps you focused and energized. Targets those areas where it\'s harder to lose fat. Enhances motor control and motivation to train harder, longer, and more efficiently. Perfect to take as a pre-workout before training, as a mid-day energy boost, or on non-training days for continued support of fat loss.*',25.00,12,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 20:51:12','2025-02-13 20:51:12'),(216,'BPI A-HD ELITE 30 CAPSULES','A BPI Sports Product\r\nPowerful Stack To Support Healthy Testosterone Levels & A Lean Physique*\r\nAnabolic & androgenic support stack\r\nDesigned for a leaner, more muscular physique\r\nSupports healthy test levels*\r\n30 servings per container\r\nMaintaining a healthy testosterone level is vital for achieving that lean, hard, muscular physique. Testosterone is the key hormone in men primarily responsible for developing strength and increasing muscle mass as well as burning fat in the body. Testosterone boosters work to optimize your workout time by giving your body the strength and focus it needs to build solid muscle. To really achieve that level of definition and vascularity, your nutrition and training need to be on point. However, sometimes that\'s still not enough. That\'s where this dynamic due of a stack swoops in to take your body where it\'s never been before: harder, stronger, and full of power!*\r\n\r\nHealthy Testosterone Levels*\r\nA Leaner More Muscular Physique*\r\nIncreased Libido & Stamina*',25.00,7,1,0.00,'2025-02-13 21:01:14','2025-02-13 21:01:14'),(217,'Ashwaganda Swanson 100 capsules','MULTIPLE HEALTH BENEFITS: A powerful mood helper, this herbal adaptogen supports healthy response to stress, aids immune system support, and helps to support energy levels. Each of our capsules contains 450mg ashwagandha root.\r\nTRUSTED FOR CENTURIES: Also known as Indian ginseng, Ashwagandha root is a potent herb and staple of traditional Ayurvedic wellness practices that is packed with bioactive compounds shown to support mental and physical vitality.\r\nDOSAGE INSTRUCTIONS: Our wellness supplements offer everyday solutions for an enhanced mind, body, and home using only the purest ingredients. For best results, take two capsules one to two times per day with water.\r\nOUR QUALITY COMMITMENT: For over 50 years, Swanson has delivered science-backed health products worldwide. Each wellness supplement is made in our GMP certified facilities, and our purity and potency testing includes independent third-party labs.',20.00,10,0,0.00,'2025-02-13 21:05:16','2025-05-19 15:18:13'),(220,'Biotech USA - Micellar Casein','Biotech USA Micellar Casein is a delicious protein powder that provides a source of slowly absorbed micellar casein and is enriched with glutamine.*\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\n\r\nUp to 22g of protein per serving\r\nEnriched with L-glutamine\r\nLow in sugar and fat\r\nGluten-free, palm oil-free, and preservative-free\r\nPotential Benefits:\r\n\r\nMay support muscle growth and maintenance*\r\nMay contribute to the maintenance of healthy bones*\r\nHOW TO USE\r\n\r\nMix 1 serving (1 scoop = 2 heaping tablespoons = 30g) with 300 ml of water. Consume before bedtime or between meals.\r\n\r\nINGREDIENTS\r\n\r\nMicellar casein concentrate (contains milk) 85%, low-fat cocoa powder, L-glutamine 5%, cream component [partially hydrogenated coconut fat, skimmed milk powder, emulsifiers (E471, E472a), glucose syrup, sucrose, milk protein, stabilizer (potassium phosphates), anti-caking agent (calcium phosphates)],',45.00,21,0,0.00,'2025-02-15 18:27:18','2025-03-26 16:26:34'),(221,'BioTech USA Hyper Mass 61servings','TriCarbo Matrix: Three different carbohydrate sources from carbohydrates with different glycemic indices\r\nProtein Blend: Three different protein sources\r\nWith micronised creatine monohydrate\r\nDietary fibres\r\nHigh protein content\r\nGluten Free\r\nHyper Mass is an excellent choice for gain lovers since you can now complement the increased caloric intake required for your growth with a product that consists of carefully selected ingredients.\r\nTricarbo Matrix is a carbohydrate complex that consists of three different carbohydrate sources with different glycemic indices.\r\nProtein Blend contains 3 different protein components that have different absorption times to ensure the protein sources required for your muscle mass growth.\r\nIn order to ensure a balanced nutritional composition each serving contains 1.4g fat. However, that’s not all, because Hyper Mass also contains 3.25 g of micronised (smaller particle size) creatine-monohydrate per serving that has more favourable properties than the traditional creatine monohydrate compound.\r\n\r\nTriCarbo Matrix, the ideal carbohydrate complex!\r\n\r\nExtra calorie intake is essential during bulking, which can primarily be achieved by the increased consumption of carbohydrates and proteins. In addition to quantity, it is also important to pay attention to the quality of your nutrient intake.\r\n\r\nTriCarbo Matrix was developed in light of the above. It contains a carbohydrate (maltodextrin) that has a high glycemic index in addition to large amounts of fibre with a low glycemic index, in the form of inulin. Moreover, it also contains corn starch, which is a modern and popular carbohydrate source.\r\n\r\nThis complex carbohydrate formula is ideal to cover the energy intake required for bulking.\r\n\r\nProtein Blend: whey protein concentrate, calcium caseinate, whey protein isolate\r\n\r\nProtein Complex contains three protein components with different absorption times. Thanks to their high biological value they provide you with an excellent protein source during bulking.\r\n\r\nBalanced nutritional composition in the service of growth\r\n\r\nIt is very important that a mass gainer product contains all three macronutrients in the right proportions and Hyper Mass meets this requirement: in addition to its high protein content, carbohydrate and fat are also featured among its ingredients.\r\n\r\nMicronised creatine monohydrate\r\n\r\nCreatine is a macromolecule comprising three amino acids (glycine, methionine, arginine); it increases physical performance during repeated short-term, high intensity exercise.\r\n\r\nLike all BioTechUSA products, Hyper Mass consists of safe and carefully selected ingredients.',70.00,4,1,0.00,'2025-02-22 18:05:26','2025-02-22 18:06:23'),(222,'Biotech USA BCAA Zero 40 servings','both men and women\r\nall kinds of training\r\nfor quick and low-calorie pre-workout amino acid supply\r\nfor retaining muscles during prolonged training\r\nfor people on a diet\r\nfor (fitness) competition preparation\r\nMUSCLE BUILDING AND ENERGISING\r\n\r\nBioTechUSA’s flavoured BCAA Zero amino acid powder contains 2:1:1 ratio of leucine, isoleucine and valine amino acids that greatly enhance each other’s effect on building muscles and energising, and they have a natural, specific proportion in muscles. We have also added vitamin B6 to the product, which contributes to normal protein and glycogen metabolism, as well as to the reduction of tiredness and fatigue.',25.00,8,1,0.00,'2025-02-22 18:10:30','2025-02-22 18:10:30'),(223,'ANIMAL PAK 44 PACKS','Animal Pak is complete nutrition loaded with 85+ highly absorbable nutrients that enhances training sessions and boosts energy in daily life through an efficient combination of vitamins, minerals, amino acids, antioxidants, digestive enzymes, carnitine, herbs and more. More than a multivitamin, Animal Pak fills your nutritional gaps ensuring you are primed for muscle growth and optimum performance as you chase your fitness goals.\r\n\r\nNew and improved formula delivers better performance and 25% less pills (now only 8 pills)\r\nConcentrated formula delivering the benefits of 12 supplements in 1 convenient packet\r\nScience-backed, advanced formula, now with less pills and easier to swallow\r\nAlso available in delicious tasting powders.\r\nWorking with nutritionists, physical science experts, and athletes, we are advancing America’s #1 training Pak, again, with a new and improved formula comprised of powerhouse ingredients designed to take your workouts to an even higher level – and delivered in an all-in-one pill pack that’s even easier and more convenient.\r\n\r\nAnimal Pak isn’t just a multivitamin, it’s a vast arsenal of over 60 key ingredients that are delivered in the right amounts at the right time, every time. Each pack has been specifically formulated to strengthen your body’s foundation to help optimize your physical and mental wellness and fitness goals — ample doses of vitamins, minerals, amino acids, herbs, and other performance optimizers to help you reach beyond your peak performance.\r\n\r\nDaily Essential Vitamins and Minerals Including A, C, B, Zinc, Calcium and More\r\nAmino Acids, Protein Complex and Liver Detox Enzymes\r\nPerformance Complex Including L-Taurine and Carnitine\r\nIncludes Spectra™, an All-Natural Blend of 29 Fruits, Vegetables, and Herbs\r\nSpirulina, Chlorella, And Ginkgo Biloba to Help Natural Immune Response\r\nEnhanced with AstraGin® to Help Improve Nutrient Bioavailability\r\nNatural Energy and Focus, with No Added Caffeine (same as a decaf cup of coffee)\r\nAvailable in Pill Packs and Great-Tasting Powders\r\nCosts Less Than Buying Individual Supplements Separately\r\n Designed for the dedicated gym goer and athlete, Animal Pak is the foundation for any active and healthy lifestyle, and able to stand up to the most intense training and rigorous dieting. Simply take one pack daily with any meal, or if you are in hard training mode, take two packs daily with your meals. Easy as that. Since Animal Pak is a foundational supplement to be taken it daily there is no need to cycle it.\r\n\r\nAnimal Pak – a convenient all-in-one pill pack, that costs less than buying individual supplements separately, is also available in great-tasting powders.',45.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-02-22 18:15:25','2025-02-22 18:15:25'),(224,'ANIMAL M-STAK 21 PACKS','Animal M-Stak is a non-hormonal, anabolic supplement pack that helps your body absorb more nutrients and build more lean muscle. Animal M-Stack’s innovative formula combats muscle breakdown and supports nutrient absorption giving you the extra push to break through workout plateaus\r\n\r\nPromotes muscle gains and naturally boosts hormone levels\r\nIncreases protein synthesis, nutrient absorption, and nitrogen retention\r\nHelps to reduce stress and improve carbohydrate metabolism\r\nAnimal M-Stak is a non-hormonal, anabolic supplement that utilizes various complexes and nutrients to help your body absorb nutrients at a more efficient rate, increase muscle gains, and support your metabolism. It has also been shown to support healthy insulin levels. Scientifically formulated for “hardgainers”, or anyone trying to build lean muscle mass, Animal M-Stak includes these key complexes:\r\nFlavone/Sterone Complex features Beta-Ecdysterone, Turkesterone, and Methoxyisoflavone to help induce anabolism creating a more primed environment for you to utilize nutrients and make more gains.\r\nInsulin Potentiating Complex contains cinnamon bark extract, alpha lipoic acid, banaba leaf extract (corosolic acid), and fenugreek feed, and supports carbohydrate metabolism to efficiently use the nutrients that you are consuming.\r\nAdaptogen Complex contains ashwagandha, kudzu and eleuthero root which reduce stress and normalize cortisol levels.\r\nAnti-Catabolic Complex with key leucine and other BCAAs has shown to keep you from breaking down muscle tissue. Don’t let catabolism (muscle breakdown) erase your gains.\r\nM-Factor Transport Complex contains ginger root, plus additional absorption enhancers 6,7-Dihydroxybergmottin and bioperine which promotes nutrient absorption assisting in the myriad of muscle growth factors in the M-Stak formula.\r\nAnimal M-Stak includes a 200mg removable caffeine pill which can be discarded for those who don’t want stimulants. For the best results, M-Stak should be cycled and combined with the right foods and proper training to be a powerful addition to your lean muscle supplement game.',45.00,7,1,0.00,'2025-02-22 18:19:14','2025-02-22 18:19:43'),(225,'R1 FISH OIL 100 SOFTGELS','R1\'s Fish Oil Softgels provide 1,000mg fish oil, yielding 180mg EPA and 120mg DHA. Our bodies can’t effectively produce these essential nutrients, so they must be obtained from seafoods or supplements made from marine sources.^',20.00,11,0,0.00,'2025-03-04 19:33:56','2025-05-21 20:10:40'),(226,'V-Shape Creatine 100 Servings','MICRONIZED & MONOHYDRATED CREATINE\r\nV-SHAPE CREATINE provides 5 Grams of pharmaceutical grade micronized and monohydrated creatine per scoop essential to increase muscle size and enhance strength during workout\r\n\r\nCategories: BULK UP, STRENGTH UP\r\nTags: BULK UP ORIGINAL LINE, STRENGTH UP ORIGINAL LINE\r\n Description Nutrition Facts HOW TO TAKE! Barcodes \r\n/// CREATINE DEFINITION\r\n5 Grams of pharmaceutical grade micronized and monohydrated creatine per scoop.\r\n\r\nCreatine is an element existing naturally in muscle cells. It helps your muscles produce energy during heavy lifting and high intensity workout.\r\n\r\nVS Supps Creatine powder has been micronized to stay in solution for a long period of time without losing its efficiency.\r\n\r\nVS Supps Creatine is unflavored and therefore you can stack it in different ways either you add it to your pre-workout BCAA shake, post-workout within your protein shake or you can consume alone with any kind of beverage juice.',23.00,3,1,0.00,'2025-03-04 19:40:23','2025-03-04 19:40:23'),(227,'GAT Sport Essentials ZMAG-T 90 Veg Capsules','Assists with raising testosterone levels and muscle performance.\r\nImproves recovery and by helping to provide a better nights sleep.\r\nWith Albion Bororganic Glycine for musculoskeletal development and hormone support.\r\nEnhance Muscle Size & strength',22.00,11,0,0.00,'2025-03-04 19:44:15','2025-05-22 15:47:15'),(228,'GAT, Testrol Gold ES, Testosterone Booster, 60 Tablets','Description\r\nAre you looking for an advanced formula that can naturally support male performance, endurance, strength and testosterone, with the added benefit of hormone regulators?  Well, look no further!  Try GAT Sport TESTROL GOLD ES and watch science and nature come together to provide you with the power to blast through your day.\r\n\r\nBalance Your Testosterone to Estrogen Ratio\r\nHelps Build Lean Muscle\r\nSupports Muscle and Male Performance',35.00,7,1,0.00,'2025-03-04 19:47:20','2025-03-04 19:47:20'),(229,'ESSENTIAL AMIN.O. ENERGY','Energy + Recovery¹\r\nEssential AMIN.O. ENERGY powder mix supports energy1 with 100mg of caffeine from natural sources per serving* and post-workout muscle recovery1 with 5g of amino acids per serving. It’s formulated for active people at every level of fitness who want a mild pre-workout energy boost or to maintain energy during physical activity1. \r\n\r\nWith more than a dozen fruit-flavors to choose from and easy mixing, it’s an easy way to bring energy1 to exercise, sports, and other physical activities – all with the quality you expect from OPTIMUM NUTRITION® – The World’s #1 Sports Nutrition Brand4.',25.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-03-25 15:06:10','2025-03-25 15:06:10'),(230,'Larry Wheels Creatine Powder - Pre Workout & Post Workout Creatine Drink - Muscle Boosting Powder for Men & Women - with Tart Cherry & Himalayan Salt, Unflavored - 120 Servings (732 Grams)','RP Creatine 120 servings \r\n5g monohydrate creatine \r\nsodium 148mg \r\nTrat cherry extract 500mg \r\nHimalayan pink salt 400mg',35.00,3,1,0.00,'2025-04-02 17:44:41','2025-04-02 17:44:41'),(231,'100% Whey Protein Plus','80 Servings\r\n\r\n• 20 grams protein\r\n\r\n• Produced through microfiltration technique for purity\r\n\r\n• Absorbs quickly into the body for maximum performance\r\n\r\n• Fuels working muscles and stimulates protein synthesis\r\n\r\n• Available in chocolate flavor\r\n\r\nChallenger Nutrition 100% Whey Protein is composed of a powerful protein matrix with whey protein concentrate, and whey protein hydrolysate. These complex proteins are balanced by muscle-building amino acids and BCAAs for maximum strength and performance.\r\n\r\nWe’re confident that this is the best whey protein on the market because our research and development team has created the ideal formula to meet the needs of today’s competitive athlete, world-class bodybuilder, and fitness buff. This is a highly focused supplement with pure ingredients and a complete mix of protein.  At Challenger, we understand what it takes to be competitive, which is why we’ve created this fast-acting whey protein product to enable you to satisfy your protein needs in accordance with your workouts and at any time of day.\r\n\r\nHere’s what Challenger whey protein shakes can do for you:\r\n\r\n• Build lean muscle\r\n\r\n• Promote strength\r\n\r\n• Improve cardiovascular function\r\n\r\n• Boost immune system\r\n\r\n• Boost energy and stamina\r\n\r\n• Synthesize natural amino acids in the body\r\n\r\n• Have a significant impact on your overall gains\r\n\r\nProtein is the most crucial element in an athlete’s diet, which is why it’s so important to choose a bodybuilder-strength whey protein that won’t let you down. Whey protein is known as a “fast protein” when consumed because it enters the bloodstream very quickly to deliver the results you crave. Whey is a dairy-based source of amino acids, which are the building blocks of protein and an essential element in any athlete’s diet.\r\n\r\nOur whey protein powder is quickly digested and absorbed in the body so that your muscles can utilize it right away. By supporting structural muscle protein synthesis, our whey protein provides the nutritional foundation for anyone who’s serious about getting in shape and growing stronger every day.\r\n\r\nIt also drastically improves muscle recovery after your workouts are complete. This means that you can work out longer and harder to reach your full potential and achieve your fitness goals. Say goodbye to muscle soreness and fatigue and get back into the gym where you belong.\r\n\r\nEach 30 gram serving of Challenger’s bodybuilding whey protein has 20 grams of protein, which is an impressive 70% concentration. This pure protein packs more protein into every scoop, with minimal fat, carbs, and sugars. Essentially, it pumps you up without weighing you down.\r\n\r\nThis isn’t your average blend of substandard whey protein with unwanted fillers. Unlike some protein providers, we don’t spike our whey protein to artificially increase the protein content or use any inferior concentrate. And at Challenger, we don’t believe in fillers – just 100% whey protein with no extra ingredients your body doesn’t need.\r\n\r\n\r\nExpertly packaged in whey protein 5.3 lb containers, our product is quick and convenient to prepare. It will also satisfy your sweet tooth so you’re less tempted to give into cravings and indulge in unhealthy foods. With Challenger, you can enjoy the sweet and satisfying flavors of whey protein powder vanilla, whey protein chocolate, and whey protein strawberry.\r\n\r\nAnd protein shakes are just the beginning. Our whey protein powder will mix well into many of your favorite recipes, such as pancakes, energy bars, muffins, and crepes. It’s also delicious when simply mixed into oatmeal, yogurt, pudding, and even coffee. The best part is that it can be used any time of the day – first thing in the morning, pre-workout, post-workout, between meals, or as a healthy snack before bed.\r\n\r\nSo if you’ve been searching for the perfect blend of power, the look no further than Challenger Nutrition 100% Whey Protein. When it comes to sports nutrition, quality is everything, so don’t trust your body to just any protein provider.\r\n\r\nThere are many different protein powders on the market, but none as effective and delicious as Challenger. All of our products undergo rigorous quality testing to take the guesswork out of supplementation and give you the results that you deserve. Challenger Nutrition 100% Whey Protein is the best way to supplement your lifestyle and a great-tasting way to fuel your passion.\r\n\r\nWhether you’re a high-performance athlete, an aspiring bodybuilder, or just trying to lose weight and gain muscle to live a healthier lifestyle, Challenger’s whey protein is the answer you’ve been looking for. Are you ready to unleash the challenger inside of you and take your fitness game to the next level?\r\n\r\nThese statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.',75.00,2,1,0.00,'2025-04-02 17:50:55','2025-04-02 17:50:55'),(232,'CREATINE MONOHYDRATE 5000MG','Creatine Monohydrate has been proven to be one of the most effective supplements for increasing muscle mass and strength. Research shows supplementing with Creatine can lead to doubling your strength and lean muscle gains when compared to training alone. Supplementing with Creatine can result in significant increases in muscle mass for both untrained individuals and elite athletes.\r\n\r\nBenefits for Daily Creatine Supplementation: \r\n\r\n- Helps Muscle Cells Produce More Energy\r\n\r\n- Promotes Muscle Growth\r\n\r\n- Improves High-Intensity Exercise Performance\r\n\r\n- May Reduce Fatigue and Tiredness\r\n\r\n- Can Improve Brain Function',23.00,3,1,0.00,'2025-04-02 18:00:49','2025-04-02 18:00:49'),(233,'CLA 95: CONJUGATED LINEOLIC ACID FOR WEIGHT LOSS','CLA Supplements\r\nWhat is a CLA Supplement?\r\nConjugated Linoleic Acid (CLA) is a remarkable dietary supplement derived from sources like safflower and sunflower oil, and found naturally in grass fed meats and dairy as well as the yolk of an egg. CLA dietary supplement works to reduce body fat by preventing fat accumulation in fat cells. Fat normally enters the fat cell through a door that is controlled by an enzyme that acts as the key.\r\nCLA 95: CONJUGATED LINEOLIC ACID FOR WEIGHT LOSS',25.00,12,1,0.00,'2025-04-11 19:08:48','2025-04-11 19:08:48'),(234,'Allflex: All-In-One Joint Formula','ALLFLEX is an advanced recovery reliever that promotes joint health and mobility and reduces the pain and inflammation associated with intense physical activity. As a proprietary blend it has been formulated for both active individuals and competitive athletes who participate in high intensity exercises.\r\nRapid Joint Recovery and Pain Management – Powered with UC•II\r\nAllflex: All-In-One Joint Formula\r\nClinically Proven and Highly Effective\r\n\r\nALLFLEX with UC-II® Collagen is clinically shown to be 348% more effective than the standard 1,500 mg Glucosamine and 1,200 mg Chondroitin combination, offering superior support for joint health, flexibility, and comfort. This formula combines UC-II® Undenatured Type-II Collagen for joint repair, 3-LASTIN™ to target inflammation, OptiMSM® for enhanced mobility, and Curcumin for free radical reduction and antioxidant protection.\r\n\r\nWhy Choose ALLFLEX?\r\n\r\nWith ALLFLEX, you can relieve joint pain, improve mobility, and enjoy long-lasting support for active lifestyles. Available in a convenient 60-capsule size, it’s a reliable addition to your daily routine.\r\n\r\nHelps Relieve Joint Pain*\r\nRestore Mobility*\r\nALLMAX Allflex: All-In-One Joint Formula is available in a 60 capsule size.',30.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-11 19:12:53','2025-04-11 19:12:53'),(235,'Citrulline Malate 2:1','MUSCULAR ENDURANCE ENHANCER\r\nCITRULLINE MALATE improves training intensity, endurance and speed of recovery. It performs this through 5 main functions:\r\nIncreases blood Arginine levels (gram for gram at double the level of Arginine).\r\nIncreases endothelial Nitric Oxide (NO) levels thereby improving vascular function and blood flow.\r\nImproves kidney bicarbonate reabsorption providing a powerful buffer against increasing muscle acidification during intense training.\r\nDetoxifies fatigued muscle tissue by removing ammonia (a toxin that can increase 3-fold during intense training).\r\nRapidly replenishes PCr (phospho-creatine) stores, PCr is a key storage of energy muscles tap into.\r\nImproves Training Intensity, Endurance & Speed of Recovery\r\nCitrulline Malate 2:1\r\nALLMAX’s CITRULLINE MALATE 2:1 WITH 2 L-CITRULLINE AMINO ACIDS BOUND TO 1 MALATE\r\nAside from assisting with delivery and absorption, the Malate has a critical function in the TCA (or Krebs) cycle that produces energy within the mitochondria. Specific research has shown a 34% increase in the rate of oxidative ATP, 20% increase in post-exercise phosphocreatine recovery and significant reduction in the sensation of fatigue.\r\n\r\nWhy Choose Citrulline Malate powder 2:1?\r\nThe fact is that most of the research on performance enhancement has been done on Citrulline Malate not just l-Citrulline powder on its own. Together with Malate, Citrulline has enhanced stability as a molecule and Malate has been shown in research to have the ability to play a role in Nitric Oxide production. Malate plays a key role in the TCA (or Tricyclic Acid) cycle (also known as the Krebs Cycle) that produces energy in the body. While it is true that Citrulline is the true “driver” of the two and that Malate is more prevalent in the body, so Citrulline Malate 2:1 provides the best of both worlds, stability and effectiveness.\r\n\r\nALLMAX Citrulline Malate is available in 300 g size.',35.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-04-11 19:17:15','2025-05-08 20:21:16'),(236,'ALLMAX Nutrition Creatine Monohydrate Powder, 1000g','BOOSTS ENERGY: Creatine is a naturally-occurring compound in the body that helps to supply energy to all cells, primarily muscle cells. Creatine is a quickly available source of energy for muscle contractions used to enhance athletic performance. Creatine has been shown to increase maximal strength and endurance by as much as 15% and up to 30% in power output and energy release in short-burst/interval sports.\r\nINCREASED MUSCLE RECOVERY: Creatine not only helps the muscle endure long-lasting, more intense training sessions, it also helps to increase muscle recovery rate.\r\nBETTER DIET: Supplementing with Creatine will help keep your performance levels high during periods of calorie reduction\r\nBETTER PUMPS: Muscle fullness or cell volumization is directly linked to the growth of the muscle. Intramuscular Creatine enhancement works to deliver better pumps and makes the muscle appear fuller.\r\nTHE ALLMAX DIFFERENCE: Allmax Pharmaceutical Grade Creatine is the ultimate in purity and safety; rigorously held to strict standards that meet or exceed 3rd-Party independent testing for WADA Banned Substances and cGMP guidelines. In addition, our Creatine is micronized to an ultra-fine, free-flowing powder. Most Creatine monohydrate powders on the market today have particles that are as much as 250% larger!',65.00,3,1,0.00,'2025-04-11 19:21:38','2025-04-11 19:21:38'),(237,'Swanson Albion Magnesium Glycinate (Magnesium Glycinate), 133 mg, 90 capsules','Swanson Albion Magnesium Glycinate delivers 133 mg of magnesium per capsule in a highly absorbable form. Key Benefits: Enhanced Absorption: Features Albion\'s magnesium glycinate chelate for superior bioavailability. Muscle and Nerve Support: Helps maintain healthy muscle function and a balanced nervous system.',23.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-12 19:05:30','2025-05-22 15:49:40'),(238,'Vitamin D-3 10,000 IU Softgels','High Potency\r\nSupports Healthy Teeth*\r\nPromotes Muscle Health*\r\nNOW Vitamin D-3 softgels supply this key vitamin in a highly-absorbable liquid softgel form. Vitamin D is normally obtained from the diet or produced by the skin from the ultraviolet energy of the sun. However, it is not abundant in food. As more people avoid sun exposure, vitamin D supplementation becomes even more necessary to ensure that your body receives an adequate supply.',25.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-12 19:10:11','2025-05-07 20:13:53'),(239,'Magnesium Malate 1000 mg Tablets','113 mg of Elemental Magnesium\r\nMagnesium is a mineral that is critical for energy production and metabolism, muscle contraction, nerve impulse transmission and bone mineralization.* It is a required cofactor for an estimated 300 enzymes.* Among the reactions catalyzed by these enzymes are fatty acid synthesis, protein synthesis, and glucose metabolism.* Malate is an important Krebs cycle intermediate, indicating that it is an important molecule in the production of cellular energy derived from carbohydrates.*',40.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-12 19:13:27','2025-05-22 15:53:03'),(240,'TruFuel L-Arginine L-Arginine 500mg – 120 Capsules','L-Arginine 500mg – 120 Capsules\r\n\r\nClean L-Arginine formula\r\n\r\nBest Results and Maximum Performance\r\n\r\nBoost your cardiovascular health and youthful appearance with L-Arginine. This supplement also supports immunity, blood pressure, bones, and tissues.',20.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-04-14 17:25:30','2025-04-14 17:25:30'),(241,'Olimp MagMAX B6 (Magnesium Citrate 687 mg + Vit. B6 and Thiamine) - 50 Tablets','Olimp MagMax B6 is a dietary supplement containing a high portion of magnesium in the form of citrate, which is a well absorbed and tolerated source of this element, enriched with vitamin B6 and thiamine. \r\n\r\nSupplements Facts:\r\nPackage Size: 50 Tablets\r\n\r\nServing Size: 1 Tablets\r\n\r\nServings Per Container: 50\r\n\r\nSupplemental Information	Amount Per Serving	% Daily Value\r\nMagnesium Citrate\r\nof which: magnesium	687 mg\r\n110 mg	*\r\n29,3%\r\nVitamin B6	2 mg	143%\r\nThiamine\r\n(Vitamin B1)	1,1 mg	100%\r\nDaily Value not established.\r\n\r\nOther ingredients:\r\nMagnesium salts of citric acid (magnesium citrate), bulking agent - microcrystalline cellulose; coating [glazing agents - polyvinyl alcohol (PVA), polyethylene glycol, talc; potato starch, anti-caking agent - magnesium salts of fatty acids; pyridoxine hydrochloride - vit. B6, thiamine hydrochloride - thiamine (vit. B1).\r\n\r\nSuggested use:\r\n1 tablet 1 to 2 times a day after a meal.\r\n\r\nCaution:\r\nThe product cannot be used as a substitute (substitute) for a varied diet. A balanced diet and a right lifestyle are important for the functioning of the human body. Do not exceed the recommended maximum daily dose. Store in a cool, dry place after opening.',15.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-14 17:53:20','2025-04-14 17:53:20'),(242,'Perfect Skin Hydro-Complex','Product description\r\nBEAUTIFUL AND ELASTIC SKIN\r\n\r\nPerfect skin hydro-complex® is a composition of active nutritional components including collagen, which helps maintain freshness and elasticity of the skin andhyaluronic acid, which participates in maintaining the skin’s healthy appearance. This supplement also contains grape seed and green tea extracts, which help in protecting the body against free radicals. Additionally, the product is enriched with vitamins and minerals such as zinc and selenium, which help to keep hair and nails in good condition.\r\n\r\nPerfect skin hydro-complex® contains active antioxidants that neutralize free radicals:\r\n\r\na grape seed extract containing (95%) proanthocyanidin (OPC) and a green tea extract with a very high content of polyphenols and catechins (EGCG)\r\nPureWay-C® – best absorbable form of vitamin C with citrus bioflavonoids\r\nVitamin E –protect cells against oxidative stress\r\nAlbion® amino acid chelates:\r\nzinc – contributes to the maintenance of normal skin\r\ncopper – contributes to normal skin pigmentation\r\nmanganese – contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress\r\nselenium – contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress\r\nThe supplement has been completed with minerals in their most bioavailable forms. Such form of amino acid chelate guarantees high grade of absorption and bioavailability. Albion Laboratories® zinc, manganese and copper amino acid chelates are of the absolute highest quality.\r\n\r\nChelation of minerals is the process of binding metallic elements by weak organic acids (amino acids). This extremely significant process enables effective absorption of the elements from the gastrointestinal tract and their distribution to the biological processes taking place with their involvement. In this form, bioelements also remain fully safe in dosing, because any excess quantities leave the body easily in the form of chelates.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nNutritional information\r\n1 capsule\r\nHydro-flex skin complex:\r\nCollagen\r\n300 mg\r\nHyaluronic acid\r\n25 mg\r\nSilica\r\n10 mg\r\nBiotin\r\n25 μg (50%*)\r\nAntioxidant perfect skin formula:\r\nGrape seed extract\r\n50 mg\r\nincluding: 95% proantocyjanidyn\r\n47,5 mg\r\nGreen tea extract\r\n50 mg\r\nincluding: 98% polyphenols, 80% catechins, 55% EGCG\r\nPatented vitamin C and citrus bioflavonoid PureWay-C®\r\n44,5 mg\r\nincluding: vitamin C\r\n40 mg (50%*)\r\nVitamin E\r\n6 mg (50%*)\r\nZinc\r\n7,5 mg (75%*)\r\nCopper\r\n500 μg (50%*)\r\nManganese\r\n1 mg (50%*)\r\nSelenium\r\n27,5 μg (50%*)\r\nL-Cistine\r\n10 mg\r\nBeta-carotene\r\n1 mg\r\nLycopene\r\n1 mg\r\n*NRV - nutrient reference value.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nIngredients: collagen (hydrolysed gelatin), green tea extract (98% polyphenols, 80% catechins, 55% EGCG), grape seed extract, mineral components (Albion® zinc amino acid chelate, Albion® manganese amino acid chelate, Albion® copper amino acid chelate, Albion® selenium amino acid chelate), vitamins (L-ascorbic acid – vitamin C PureWay-C®, dl-á-tocopherol– vitamin E, D-biotin), sodium hyaluronate, colloidal silica, beta-carotene, lycopene, L-cystine, citrus bioflavonoids, microcrystalline cellulose – bulking agent, magnesium stearate – anti-caking agent, capsule (gelatin – sheath component, colour: E172, E104, E110).\r\n\r\nPurpose\r\nThe product is recommended for women who care about their looks as an agent enhancing appearance of the skin\r\n\r\nDosage\r\nRecommended use: 1 capsule a day between meals.\r\n\r\nDo not exceed the recommended daily dose.\r\nFood supplements should not be used as a substitute for a varied and balanced diet.\r\nA varied and balanced diet and a healthy lifestyle are recommended.\r\nKeep out of reach of children.',19.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-14 17:56:41','2025-04-14 17:56:41'),(243,'Calcium D3 Forte','Product description\r\nCALCIUM D3 Forte is a food supplement in the form of film-coated tablets, containing a high dose of calcium and vitamin D – components having a synergistic action important in many processes in the body.\r\n\r\nScientific studies have proved that:\r\n\r\nCalcium:\r\n\r\nis needed for the maintenance of normal teeth\r\ncontributes to normal energy-yielding metabolism\r\ncontributes to normal neurotransmission\r\ncontributes to normal muscle function\r\ncontributes to the normal function of digestive enzymes\r\ncontributes to normal blood coagulation\r\nVitamin D:\r\n\r\ncontributes to normal absorption/utilisation of calcium and phosphorus\r\ncontributes to normal blood calcium levels\r\ncontributes to the maintenance of normal bones and teeth\r\nhas a role in the process of cell division- contributes to the maintenance of normal muscle function\r\ncontributes to the normal function of the immune system\r\nAn adequate content of calcium and vitamin D in the diet is especially important during the period of rapid growth and achieving peak bone mass, during pregnancy and lactation, after fractures and injuries, as well as for women during menopause and for the elderly, in whom bone resorption processes prevail the processes of bone formation. It is noteworthy that the amount of vitamin D obtained from in-body synthesis undergoes significant fluctuations depending on exposure to sunlight, which might result in limited supply due to low sun exposure. contributes to normal absorption/utilisation of calcium and phosphorus contributes to normal blood calcium levels contributes to the maintenance of normal bones and teeth has a role in the process of cell division- contributes to the maintenance of normal muscle function contributes to the normal function of the immune system An adequate content of calcium and vitamin D in the diet is especially important during the period of rapid growth and achieving peak bone mass, during pregnancy and lactation, after fractures and injuries, as well as for women during menopause and for the elderly, in whom bone resorption processes prevail the processes of bone formation. It is noteworthy that the amount of vitamin D obtained from in-body synthesis undergoes significant fluctuations depending on exposure to sunlight, which might result in limited supply due to low sun exposure.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nNutritional information\r\n1 capsule\r\nCalcium\r\n625 mg (78%*)\r\nVitamin D\r\n10 µg (200%*)\r\n*NRV - nutrient reference value.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nIngredients: Calcium carbonate, glazing agents – Polyvinyl alcohol, Polyethylene glycol, Talc; anti-caking agent – Magnesium stearate, bulking agent – crosslinked Sodium carboxymethyl cellulose, Cholecalciferol – Vitamin D.\r\n\r\nThe maximum calcium intake from all sources for adults, including pregnant and breastfeeding women, is 2500 mg (milligrams) per day. The safe maximum vitamin D intake from all sources for adults and children over 11 years of age is 100 µg (micrograms) per day, and for children from 1 year to 10 years it is 50µg.\r\n\r\nPurpose\r\nProduct is intended: as a food supplement, providing daily demand for calcium and vitamin D.\r\n\r\nDosage\r\nRecommended use: : 1-2 tablets a day, after a meal, or according to your physician’s recommendation. Tablets should be taken with an adequate amount of water.\r\n\r\nDo not exceed the stated recommended daily dose. Food supplements should not be used as a substitute for a varied and balanced diet. Excessive consumption may cause a laxative effect. Keep out of reach of children. A varied and balanced diet and a healthy lifestyle are recommended.\r\n\r\nContraindications: Hypersensitivity to any of the ingredients. In the case of nephrolithiasis, kidney failure and hyperparathyroidism, the use of this product should be made in consultation with physician. Do not use together with other products with a high content of calcium and vitamin D. Not recommended to young children due to the risk of choking',15.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-14 18:19:49','2025-04-14 18:19:49'),(244,'Kolagen Activ Plus','DESCRIPTION\r\nIndication:\r\nKolagen Activ Plus is a food supplement with collagen, vitamins and minerals. Formulated with minerals such as calcium and magnesium to maintain normal bones, cartilage and skin.\r\n\r\nHow To Use:\r\nTake 4 tablets, 2 times a day between meals.\r\n\r\nFamilialist\'s Recommendation:\r\nHighly recommended, Collagen hydrolysate a natural component of the skin that helps the skin to preserve its firmness and elasticit.\r\n\r\n80 TABLETS',20.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-04-14 18:23:26','2025-04-14 18:23:26'),(245,'BioTechUSA L-Arginine 300 g','DESCRIPTION\r\nIndication:\r\nImproves blood flow, vascularity and endurance.\r\nIncrease the level of testosterone and Growth hormone.Enhance muscle recover \r\n\r\nHow to use:\r\nMix 1 serving of powder (4 g = 2 flat measuring spoon = half a tablespoon) with \r\n250 ml water. Take 2 servings a day, one 30 minutes before workout.\r\n\r\nOn rest days drink the powder before going to sleep.\r\n\r\nFor best result, use a shaker bottle.\r\n\r\nDo not exceed recommended daily allowance\r\n \r\n Size: 150 Servings',35.00,6,0,0.00,'2025-04-15 16:59:02','2025-05-14 16:37:15'),(246,'Universal Beef Aminos 400 tablets','100% Beef Aminos™ is a high potency, natural product derived from the highest quality beef protein isolate and pure desiccated Argentine beef liver. This superior nutritional product contains a full spectrum of key amino acids (EAAs & BCAAs). This formula harnesses the true anabolic potential of beef and is ideal support for anyone looking to add lean mass.',35.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-04-19 15:56:53','2025-04-19 15:56:53'),(247,'Russian Bear Gainer','RUSSIAN BEAR 10000 – GUARANTEE YOUR MONSTER RESULTS BY GAINING TRUE MASS\r\nRussian Bear Nutrition, known as “The Home of Hardcore Supplements”, develops its products since 1990 for hardcore bodybuilders, who aim for massive muscle mass and triple muscle growth.\r\n\r\nFor Russian Bear, Bodybuilders’ satisfaction is the ultimate goal, which the brand thrives to achieve through its innovative products designed by state-of-the-art facilities by scientists, technicians and trainers. The brand keeps delivering what it has promised from products that deliver massive muscle gains, triple muscle growth and high testosterone levels for ultimate gains.\r\n\r\nMassive muscle gains and bulking up don’t just simply happen. You need an advanced formula that is enriched with high-quality protein, complex carbohydrates and essential vitamins and minerals. Russian Bear 10000 Weight Gainer is a protein-based weight gaining formula that will provide you with massive muscle and weight gains.\r\n\r\nIncreased caloric intake can’t always be obtained from food, especially for bulking up and weight gain. Each scoop of Russian Bear 10000 Weight Gainer grants you 1860 calories, which could double your muscle mass during bulking up stages. The ultimate weight gainer also contains 118g of high-quality protein, to fulfill each and every athlete’s needs of protein supplementation.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the perfect amount of calories and protein, Russian Bear 10000 Weight Gainer provides 81g of amino acids that are enough to prepare you for your next workout with recovered muscles, to give your all at the gym and achieve more gains.\r\n\r\nWe know how hard you train, and want to give you the gains you deserve. So don’t hesitate when it comes to weight and muscle mass gains, and try Russian Bear 10000 Weight Gainer Now!\r\n\r\nDIRECTIONS\r\nMix 6 scoops (470g) of Russian Bear 10000 (each scoop is 78.3g x 6 = 470g) with 750 ml skimmed milk or water or your favorite juice.\r\nEach scoop can be mixed with 150 ml -200 ml. You can mix 1-2 scoops in the morning (78.3g-156.6g), 1-2 scoops in the afternoon (78.3g-156.6g) and 1-2 scoops after workout (78.3g-156.6g).\r\nPlease don’t exceed 6 scoops per day and make sure to drink at least 1.5 liter of water during the day.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nMaltodextrin, waxy maize, fructose, l-glycine, creatine monohydrate, l-glutamine, l-leucine, l-isoleucine, l-valine, creatine ethyl ester, whey protein concentrate, whey protein isolate, micellar casein, milk protein isolate, sunflower and/or soy oil powder, conjugated linoleic acid powder, medium chain triglycerides (from coconut), cocoa powder, gum blend (cellulose, xanthan, carrageenan), natural and artificial flavours, natural bitter masker, acesulfame potassium (e950), sucralose (e955).',80.00,4,1,0.00,'2025-04-19 16:33:43','2025-04-19 16:33:43'),(248,'Essential Amino 9','When it comes to supporting muscle building and maintenance, these nine \"essential\" amino acids are aptly titled. Since they can\'t be synthesized within our bodies, they must be obtained through nutritional sources. Essential Amino 9 delivers 7.5g of essential amino acids in every serving, plus added electrolytes for hydration.',30.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 19:21:07','2025-05-07 19:21:07'),(249,'Nature\'s Truth Biotin 10000mcg | 120 Fast Dissolve Tablets | Maximum Strength | Natural Berry Flavor | Vegan, Non-GMO & Gluten Free Supplement','About this item\r\nMAXIMUM STRENGTH BIOTIN: Receive 10,000 mcg of Biotin, an essential B Vitamin\r\nVEGAN FORMULA: Fast dissolve tablets are a delicious natural berry flavor\r\nHONEST & TRANSPARENT: Nature’s Truth is committed to delivering the best quality wellness products\r\nMADE WITHOUT: Gluten, Yeast, Milk, Lactose, Soy, Artificial Flavor, Preservatives, and Non-GMO',25.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 19:28:57','2025-05-22 15:56:19'),(250,'Nature\'s Truth D3 1000 IU | 250 Softgels | Essential Vitamin D | Non-GMO & Gluten Free Supplement','About this item\r\nESSENTIAL VITAMIN D3: Receive 1,000 IU or 25 mcg of Vitamin D (as D3 Cholecalciferol) each day\r\nVALUE SIZE: Each bottle contains 50 more quick release softgels than the standard bottle\r\nHONEST & TRANSPARENT: Nature’s Truth is committed to delivering the best quality wellness products\r\nNATURALLY FREE OF: Gluten, Wheat, Yeast, Milk, Lactose, Soy, Artificial Color, Flavor, Sweetener & Preservatives, and Non-GMO',23.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 19:42:46','2025-05-22 16:27:30'),(252,'Nature\'s Truth Vitamin D3 2000 IU Softgels | 150 Count | High Potency | Non-GMO and Gluten Free Supplement','About this item\r\nVITAMIN D3 SUPPLEMENT: Delivers 50 mcg (2000 IU) per softgel\r\nSUNSHINE VITAMIN: Get your daily dose of Vitamin D3 with Nature\'s Truth premium supplement!\r\nPURITY & POTENCY: Nature\'s Truth delivers high-quality ingredients tested for purity and potency.\r\nNATURE\'S TRUTH SUPPLEMENTS: Backed by three generations of Vitamin Innovators for unrivaled quality\r\nNATURALLY FREE OF: Gluten, Wheat, Yeast, Milk, Lactose, Soy, Artificial Color & Flavoring & NON-GMO',25.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 19:50:21','2025-05-22 16:41:44'),(253,'Nature\'s Truth Vitamin B Complex | Plus B12 | 90 Tablets | High Potency | Vegan and Non-GMO Supplement','About this item\r\nB-COMPLEX VITAMINS: Receive the daily recommended amount of Vitamin B-1, B-2 & B-12.\r\nVEGAN TABLETS: Easy-to-take tablets are vegan friendly, suitable for all lifestyles.\r\nHONEST & TRANSPARENT: Nature’s Truth is committed to delivering the best quality wellness products.\r\nEXPERTS YOU CAN TRUST: Backed by three generations of Vitamin Innovators for unrivaled quality.\r\nMADE WITHOUT: Milk, Lactose, Soy, Artificial Color, Sweetener & Flavor, and Non-GMO.',18.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 19:53:37','2025-05-22 16:44:50'),(254,'Nature\'s Truth Vitamin B Complex Plus Vitamin C | 100 Caplets | Vegan, Non-GMO & Gluten Free Supplement','About this item\r\nCOMPLETE COMPLEX: Features a balanced blend of B Vitamins plus Vitamin C for maximum support!\r\nOPTIMAL FORM: Our Coated Caplets make it super convenient to receive 100% of your daily value\r\nPURITY & POTENCY: Nature\'s Truth delivers high-quality ingredients tested for purity and potency\r\nEXPERTS YOU CAN TRUST: Backed by three generations of Vitamin Innovators for unrivaled quality\r\nNATURALLY FREE OF: Gluten, Wheat, Yeast, Milk, Lactose, Artificial Flavor & Sweetener & NON-GMO',18.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 19:55:56','2025-05-22 16:46:48'),(255,'Nature\'s Truth Longjack Tongkat Ali | 1600mg | 120 Capsules | Max Strength Formula for Men | Non-GMO & Gluten Free Supplement','What Is Longjack Tongkat Ali?\r\n\r\nLongjack Tongkat Ali is a traditional herb that is derived from the root of Eurycoma longifolia Jack, a flowering green shrub that is native to southeast Asia. Also known as “Tongkat Ali,” this herb has been widely revered by men for centuries, with diverse cultures finding it valuable for their encounters.\r\n\r\nNature’s Truth Longjack Tongkat Ali Capsules\r\n\r\nThese concentrated quick release capsules deliver the equivalent of 1,600 mg of Longjack per serving, from 80 mg of a 20:1 extract.** This maximum strength male formula provides quality plant-based support that is not usually found in large amounts within typical diets. Men all over the world have taken Tongkat Ali in anticipation of crucial moments.\r\n\r\nNature’s Truth: Where Wellness Begins\r\n\r\nOur mission at Nature’s Truth is to meet your wellness needs with products that go above and beyond. Nature’s Truth provides supplements in various delivery forms, such as capsules, softgels, chewables, tablets, powders, liquids, and gummies to suit every preference. Our Longjack Tongkat Ali capsules are non-GMO, and free of gluten, wheat, yeast, milk, lactose, soy, artificial color, artificial flavor, artificial sweetener, and preservatives.\r\n\r\n**Equivalent from 80 mg of 20:1 extract per serving.\r\n\r\nDirections: For adult men, take two (2) quick release capsules daily, preferably with a meal.',30.00,7,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 20:07:07','2025-05-07 20:07:07'),(256,'Women\'s Multivitamin with Collagen 70 Gummies','What Are Multivitamins?\r\n\r\nMultivitamins are comprised of multiple vitamins, minerals, and nutrients in the convenience of one formula. Taking a multivitamin each day is a wonderful and simple way to be proactive in your daily routine. \r\n\r\nNature’s Truth Women’s Multivitamin Gummies\r\n\r\nNature’s Truth Women’s Multivitamin Gummies are a convenient way to reap the benefits of an array of vitamins and minerals in one easy-to-take formula. Each serving contains a blend of 10 vitamins and minerals in delicious mixed berry-flavored gummies. Formulated specifically for women, these gummies include collagen – a favorite ingredient among beauty supplements.\r\n\r\nNature’s Truth: Where Wellness Begins\r\n\r\nOur mission at Nature’s Truth is to meet your wellness needs with products that go above and beyond. Nature’s Truth provides supplements in various delivery forms, such as capsules, softgels, chewables, tablets, powders, liquids, and gummies to suit every preference. Our Women’s Multivitamin plus Collagen is non-GMO, and free of gluten, wheat, yeast, milk, lactose, soy, and artificial sweetener.\r\n\r\nDirections: For adults, take two (2) gummies daily, preferably with a meal. Do not exceed recommended dosage.',30.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-07 20:09:24','2025-05-07 20:09:24'),(257,'Animal Stak','Animal Stak is a comprehensive, natural, anabolic, performance supplement designed to help men build lean muscle. The supplement is packed with five unique complexes to boost natural testosterone levels and support growth hormone (GH) elevation giving you increased muscle mass, strength, energy, and vitality.\r\nNaturally enhance output of testosterone while lowering estrogen levels\r\nIncreased muscle mass, endurance, strength, energy, and vitality\r\nBetter pump, improved blood flow, and stronger muscles\r\nAnimal Stak is developed for the bodybuilder and elite strength athlete that is looking to break through plateaus and personal records. Our formula includes five unique complexes that will help you boost natural testosterone levels and elevated growth hormone support to give you increased muscle mass, strength, energy, and vitality including:\r\nPro Testosterone Complex is packed with Tribulus Terrestris extract, eurycoma longifolia, maca root extract and more to help take your natural testosterone levels and amplify them.\r\nAromatase Combating Complex that includes, Resveratrol, DIM and calcium D-glucarate, and may help support healthy estrogen levels so you don’t experience side effects related to heightened testosterone levels.\r\nGrowth Hormone Support is the complex that directly involves your body’s natural growth hormone output to give you a better pump and improved blood flow along with increased muscle fullness and better body composition.\r\nHormone Amplifying Blend includes Carnitine, Agmatine Sulfate and Astaxanthin among other ingredients to enhance testosterone and the growth hormone\r\nlevels.\r\nRestorative Support Complex which contains a key blend of milk thistle extract, astragalus, ashwagandha extract, alpha lipoic acid and Co-Q10 to provide internal organ support.\r\nThrough these five unique complexes, Animal Stak will push you closer to your goals of obtaining size and strength, while helping to elevate natural testosterone and growth hormone levels to help you build lean muscle.',45.00,7,1,0.00,'2025-05-22 15:05:51','2025-05-22 15:05:51'),(258,'Animal Flex The Complete Joint Support Supplement','The award-winning joint support supplement pack that helps repair, protect, and maintain joint health and function. Animal Flex rebuilds and lubricates joints with Glucosamine, Chondroitin, MSM, and a full complex of joint health ingredients including hyaluronic acid and flaxseed oil. Available in convenient all-in-one pill packs and great tasting powders.\r\nProtect and repair joints with Glucosamine, Chondroitin and MSM\r\nComprehensive joint health matrix improves joint function, elasticity, flexibility\r\nAvailable in convenient all-in-one daily pill packs and great tasting powders\r\nAlso available in delicious tasting powders.\r\nAnimal Flex helps strengthen joints and ligaments, shielding them from the daily wear and tear brought about rigorous training, regardless of the sport. The ingredients in Animal Flex can help maintain healthy joint function, elasticity, and flexibility with active ingredients that provide the basic building blocks that are required to maintain human structural integrity to keep your body’s foundation strong\r\nEach pack of Animal Flex is formulated with several key protective complexes for joint health:\r\nJoint Construction Complex is a potent formula to help repair and protect connective tissue. As a joint \'constructor\', Animal Flex provides joints with essential raw materials such as glucosamine (two forms), MSM, and chondroitin. These nutrients aid in the rebuilding of cartilage and naturally protect and restore joint health while strengthening the underlying cartilage and connective tissue.\r\nJoint Lubrication Complex to help cushion the joints from stressful activities and is formulated with Hyaluronic acid (HA), patented cetyl myristoleate (CMO), and flaxseed oil to provide the lubricant needed to coat your joints and protect them from the constant grind of training excess and resulting stiffness. These potent joint lubricators naturally restore the oils present in the synovial fluid to make joints work smoothly and painlessly.\r\nJoint Support Complex to help promote rehabilitation and reduce soreness utilizes potent natural herbal extracts to help address the free radical load— a consequence of inflammation of the joints. Herbs and extracts like turmeric, boswellia and ginger root have been shown to help inhibit pro-inflammatory metabolites, which leads to a strong and prolonged anti-inflammatory effect which is critical for maintaining pain free joints.\r\nEssential Vitamin and Mineral Blend to underscore optimal joint health is specialized to provide the basic essential micro-nutrients needed for joint health including Vitamins C, E, zinc, selenium and manganese.\r\nWhether you’re a lifter, runner, cross fitter or fighter, your joints take a pounding from your rigorous workout regime and can ache just from everyday life. Just take one pill packet of Animal Flex per day to help protect, repair and restore your joints and cartilage. Flex is also available in great tasting powders.',45.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-22 15:12:41','2025-05-22 15:12:41'),(259,'Animal Flex','Joint and Bone health support formula\r\nAnimal Flex, the award-winning joint support supplement, helps repair, protect, and maintain joint and bone health and function in a great tasting powder. Animal Flex rebuilds and lubricates joints. With additional ingredients such as Glucosamine, Chondroitin, MSM, and a complete blend including turmeric root curcumin, collagen, hyaluronic acid, and ginger root. Available in great tasting powders and convenient all-in-one pill packs.\r\nProtect and repair joints\r\n44 Packets\r\nComprehensive joint health matrix improves joint function, elasticity, flexibility\r\nSo effective that you only need a single Pack per day \r\nYou may also like',45.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-22 15:16:03','2025-05-22 15:16:03'),(260,'TruFule HMB 120 Tablet','HMB stands for beta-Hydroxy \r\nbeta-Methylbutyrate. it\'s a natural compound produced in the body when the amino Leucine is broken down. Leucineis one of the essential amino acid found in dietary proteins. \r\n   Reduce muscle breakdown \r\n   Supports muscle growth \r\n   Improves recovery \r\n   Increase strength',25.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-05-22 15:36:09','2025-05-22 15:36:09'),(261,'Nature\'s Truth Vitamin D3 5000 IU (125 mcg) | Extra Strength 130 Quick Release Softgels','Vitamin D3 is an essential vitamin that is known as the “Sunshine Vitamin” because of the body’s ability to naturally produce it after exposure to sunlight. Vitamin D3 is beneficial especially to those who spend a lot of time indoors or those who wear sunscreen regularly to protect their skin while outdoors.',27.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-22 16:36:45','2025-05-22 16:36:45'),(262,'Nature\'s Truth Fishoil 90 softgels 720mg','FISH OIL: Receive 2,400 mg of Fish Oil per serving, which includes 720 mg of Omega-3 fatty acids\r\nODORLESS FORMULA: These lemon flavored softgels combat fish burps\r\nHONEST & TRANSPARENT: Nature’s Truth is committed to delivering the best quality wellness products\r\nEXPERTS YOU CAN TRUST: Backed by three generations of Vitamin Innovators for unrivaled quality\r\nNATURALLY FREE OF: Gluten, Wheat, Milk, Lactose, Artificial Sweetener & Color, and Non-GMO',25.00,11,1,0.00,'2025-05-26 20:50:09','2025-05-26 20:50:09'),(263,'Celltech Creactor HCL 120 servings','Maximum Potency Creatine: MuscleTech Cell-Tech Creactor is science-backed, delivering potent micro-doses of creatine and creatine hydrocholoride (HCl) for an enhanced experience. Unflavored. 120 scoops per tub.\r\nAdvanced Formula: Creatine is found naturally in muscles and enhances their ability to regenerate ATP so you can recover faster. Each serving delivers 750MG of ultra-pure HCl and 750MG of free-acid creatine, the purest form free of acids and salts.\r\nEnhance Lean Muscle, Strength & Performance: Cell-Tech Creactor is formulated to increase muscle strength, increase performance and enhance size with just two super-concentrated scoops a day.\r\nUltra-Pure Ingredients: Cell-Tech Creator delivers free-acid creatine with absolutely zero fillers, carbs or fats — so you never have to load or cycle it.\r\nPushing the Limits of Science and Human Potential: MuscleTech’s commitment to research, development, and innovation is the reason we continue to be an elite name for redefining performance through cutting-edge products and high-quality ingredients.',35.00,3,1,0.00,'2025-05-26 20:55:08','2025-05-26 20:55:08'),(264,'RED REX CREATINE 5000MG UNFLAVORED','Description\r\n\r\nBig Ramy Labs Red Rex Creatine\r\nCreatine monohydrate is a popular dietary supplement that is widely used by athletes and bodybuilders to enhance their physical performance and build muscle mass.\r\n\r\nComposition\r\nCreatine Monohydrate is a naturally occurring compound that is found in small amounts in animal products such as meat and fish.\r\n\r\nIt is also synthesized in the body from the amino acids glycine, arginine, and methionine. Creatine monohydrate is typically sold in powder form and is intended to be mixed with water or a sports drink.\r\n\r\nIngredients\r\nEach scoop contains 5 gm of pure Creatine Monohydrate.\r\n\r\nAllergen Warning\r\nMade in a facility that processes milk, soy, egg, sesame, peanuts, tree nuts, fish, crustaceans, shellfish oils, and wheat products.\r\n\r\nDirections of Use\r\nMix 1 scoop with 237 to 355 ml of water or your favorite beverage.\r\n\r\nDo not exceed the recommended daily dose.\r\n\r\nPurpose\r\nCreatine monohydrate can help to increase muscle mass by promoting the growth of muscle fibers.\r\nCreatine monohydrate can improve athletic performance by increasing the amount of energy available to the muscles during high-intensity activities.\r\nCreatine monohydrate can help to reduce fatigue during high-intensity activities by increasing the levels of creatine phosphate in the muscles.\r\nCreatine monohydrate can help to improve recovery by reducing muscle damage and inflammation after exercise.',20.00,3,1,0.00,'2025-05-26 21:00:03','2025-05-26 21:00:03'),(265,'Cellucor C4 Original Pre-workout 50 Servings','C4 Original Pre-workout 50 Servings New & Improved\r\nReady to crush your fitness goals? The new and improved C4 Original Pre-workout formula is your secret weapon for every workout. We have elevated our classic blend, now featuring 200mg of caffeine for explosive energy and 2g of CarnoSyn® Beta-Alanine to boost muscular endurance, helping you power through even the toughest sets. Our powerful trio of L-Citrulline, L-Arginine, and Creatine Nitrate enhances nitric oxide production for incredible pumps and strength. Plus, with AI-powered PeptiPump®—exclusive to C4—for improved performance and enhanced focus from Huperzine A, the revamped C4 Original formula will keep you hitting every rep as hard as the first!\r\n\r\nC4 Original Pre-workout Key Features:\r\nHARD HITTING ENERGY ™: Amp up your gym session with 200mg of caffeine for powerful, explosive energy.*\r\nMUSCULAR ENDURANCE^: Tackle your most challenging workouts with CarnoSyn® Beta-Alanine for enhanced endurance support.*\r\nAI-POWERED PEPTIDES: PeptiPump® is a designer peptide powered by AI, available exclusively in C4.*\r\nSHARPENED FOCUS: Maintain your concentration from the first rep to the last with the combined power of Huperzine A and caffeine.*\r\nDELICIOUS FLAVOR: With billions of servings sold, C4® has set the benchmark for outstanding taste for over a decade.\r\nC4: With 20 years of sports nutrition experience, we’ve elevated the standard with our innovative range of supplements.\r\nC4 Pre-workout Ingredients:\r\n200mg Caffeine: Intense Energy & Enhanced Focus.\r\nVelox® Performance Blend: A patented combination of L-Citrulline and L-Arginine designed to support performance, pump, and recovery.\r\nCreatine Nitrate ( NO3-T®): Enhances pump and boosts training performance. \r\nCarnoSyn® Beta-Alanine: Clinically studied ingredient that helps support muscular endurance and combat muscular fatigue. \r\nPeptiPump® Bioactive Lentil Peptides: Combined with VELOX® Performance Blend and Creatine Nitrate to enhance pump and improve training performance.\r\nHuperzine A: In conjunction with caffeine, supports enhanced Focus.',35.00,9,1,0.00,'2025-05-27 14:55:27','2025-05-27 14:55:27'),(266,'MUSCLTECH 100% GLUTAMINE 60 SERVINGS','About this item\r\nFor Muscle Metabolism & Recovery: MuscleTech Platinum 100% Glutamine powder replenishes what\'s lost during intense exercise. Glutamine is an essential amino acid that supports metabolic function and recovery. Unflavored. 60 servings.\r\nUltra-Pure Ingredients: Each serving contains 5g of premium glutamine with no fillers or additives. Platinum 100% Glutamine is odorless, mixes easily on its own, and with no flavor, it seamlessly fits into your supplement routine.\r\nRestore & Replenish Plasma Glutamine: Glutamine makes up over 20% of your body\'s amino acids and is used in various metabolic functions like energy production. Platinum 100% Glutamine is designed to help replenish what is lost during intense training.\r\nDirections: Take 1 scoop with water or your favorite beverage. Consume 2 servings daily for best results.\r\nPushing the Limits of Science and Human Potential: MuscleTech’s commitment to research, development, and innovation is the reason we continue to be an elite name for redefining performance through cutting-edge products and high-quality ingredients.',30.00,6,1,0.00,'2025-05-27 15:02:33','2025-05-27 15:02:33'),(267,'MR HYDE NIGHTMARE','HYDE® Nightmare is a pre-workout powder, formulated for high-performance athletes who endure an excessive amount of physical and mental stress. Driven by clinically researched ingredients to improve muscular and mental performance, HYDE® Nightmare also replenishes lost fluids during rigorous activity.',28.00,9,1,0.00,'2025-05-27 15:11:30','2025-05-27 15:11:30');
